4114 
4115 bool OS::Core::Compiler::compile()
4116 {
4117  OS_ASSERT(!prog_strings_table && !prog_numbers_table && !prog_filename_string_index);
4118  OS_ASSERT(!prog_functions.count && !prog_numbers.count && !prog_strings.count && !prog_debug_info.count);
4119 
4120  Scope * scope = NULL;
4121  if(tokenizer->isError()){
4122  setError(ERROR_SYNTAX, NULL);
4123  }else if(!readToken()){
4124  setError(ERROR_EXPECT_TOKEN, recent_token);
4125  }else{
4126  scope = expectTextExpression();
4127  }
4128  if(scope){
4129  prog_strings_table = allocator->core->newTable(OS_DBG_FILEPOS_START);
4130  prog_numbers_table = allocator->core->newTable(OS_DBG_FILEPOS_START);
4131 
4132  Expression * exp = postCompileExpression(scope, scope);
4133  if(exp){
4134  OS_ASSERT(exp->type == EXP_TYPE_FUNCTION);
4135 
4136  OS::String filename = tokenizer->getTextData()->filename;
4137  bool is_eval = filename.isEmpty() || !tokenizer->getTextData()->is_real_file;
4138 
4139  if((!is_eval || allocator->core->settings.create_text_eval_opcodes) &&
4140  allocator->core->settings.create_text_opcodes)
4141  {
4142  Buffer dump(allocator);
4143  OS_ASSERT(dynamic_cast<Scope*>(exp));
4144  exp->debugPrint(dump, this, dynamic_cast<Scope*>(exp), 0);
4145  OS::String dump_filename = allocator->getTextOpcodesFilename(filename);
4146  FileStreamWriter(allocator, dump_filename).writeBytes(dump.buffer.buf, dump.buffer.count);
4147  }
4148  if(allocator->core->settings.create_debug_info){
4149  prog_filename_string_index = cacheString(filename);
4150  }else{
4151  prog_filename_string_index = cacheString(String(allocator));
4152  }
4153  if(writeOpcodes(scope, exp)){
4154  MemStreamWriter mem_writer(allocator);
4155  saveToStream(&mem_writer);
4156 
4157  if(!is_eval && allocator->core->settings.create_compiled_file){
4158  OS::String compiled_filename = allocator->getCompiledFilename(filename);
4159  FileStreamWriter(allocator, compiled_filename).writeBytes(mem_writer.buffer.buf, mem_writer.buffer.count);
4160  }
4161 
4162  Program * prog = new (malloc(sizeof(Program) OS_DBG_FILEPOS)) Program(allocator);
4163  // prog->filename = tokenizer->getTextData()->filename;
4164 
4165  MemStreamReader mem_reader(NULL, mem_writer.buffer.buf, mem_writer.buffer.count);
4166  prog->loadFromStream(&mem_reader);
4167 
4168  prog->pushStartFunction();
4169  prog->release();
4170 
4171  allocator->deleteObj(exp);
4172 
4173  return true;
4174  }
4175  }
4176  OS_ASSERT(error);
4177  }
4178 
4179  Buffer dump(allocator);
4180  dump += OS_TEXT("compiler error");
4181  switch(error){
4182  default:
4183  dump += OS_TEXT(" unknown");
4184  break;
4185 
4186  case ERROR_SYNTAX:
4187  if(tokenizer->isError()){
4188  OS_ASSERT(!error_token);
4189  switch(tokenizer->getErrorCode()){
4190  case Tokenizer::ERROR_MULTI_LINE_COMMENT: // multi line comment not end
4191  dump += OS_TEXT(" TOKENIZER_MULTI_LINE_COMMENT");
4192  break;
4193 
4194  case Tokenizer::ERROR_CONST_STRING: // string not end
4195  dump += OS_TEXT(" TOKENIZER_CONST_STRING");
4196  break;
4197 
4198  case Tokenizer::ERROR_CONST_STRING_ESCAPE_CHAR: // string escape error
4199  dump += OS_TEXT(" TOKENIZER_CONST_STRING_ESCAPE_CHAR");
4200  break;
4201 
4202  default:
4203  OS_ASSERT(false);
4204  // no break
4205 
4206  case Tokenizer::ERROR_SYNTAX:
4207  dump += OS_TEXT(" TOKENIZER_SYNTAX");
4208  break;
4209  }
4210  }else{
4211  dump += OS_TEXT(" SYNTAX");
4212  }
4213  break;
4214 
4215  case ERROR_NESTED_ROOT_BLOCK:
4216  dump += OS_TEXT(" NESTED_ROOT_BLOCK");
4217  break;
4218 
4219  case ERROR_LOCAL_VAL_NOT_DECLARED:
4220  dump += OS_TEXT(" LOCAL_VAL_NOT_DECLARED");
4221  break;
4222 
4223  case ERROR_VAR_NAME:
4224  dump += OS_TEXT(" VAR_NAME");
4225  break;
4226 
4227  case ERROR_EXPECT_TOKEN_TYPE:
4228  dump += OS_TEXT(" EXPECT_TOKEN_TYPE ");
4229  dump += Tokenizer::getTokenTypeName(expect_token_type);
4230  break;
4231 
4232  case ERROR_EXPECT_TOKEN_STR:
4233  dump += OS_TEXT(" EXPECT_TOKEN_STR ");
4234  dump += expect_token;
4235  break;
4236 
4237  case ERROR_EXPECT_TOKEN:
4238  dump += OS_TEXT(" EXPECT_TOKEN");
4239  break;
4240 
4241  case ERROR_EXPECT_VALUE:
4242  dump += OS_TEXT(" EXPECT_VALUE");
4243  break;
4244 
4245  case ERROR_EXPECT_WRITEABLE:
4246  dump += OS_TEXT(" EXPECT_WRITEABLE");
4247  break;
4248 
4249  case ERROR_EXPECT_GET_OR_SET:
4250  dump += OS_TEXT(" EXPECT_GET_OR_SET");
4251  break;
4252 
4253  case ERROR_EXPECT_EXPRESSION:
4254  dump += OS_TEXT(" EXPECT_EXPRESSION");
4255  break;
4256 
4257  case ERROR_EXPECT_FUNCTION_SCOPE:
4258  dump += OS_TEXT(" EXPECT_FUNCTION_SCOPE");
4259  break;
4260 
4261  case ERROR_EXPECT_CODE_SEP_BEFORE_NESTED_BLOCK:
4262  dump += OS_TEXT(" EXPECT_CODE_SEP_BEFORE_NESTED_BLOCK");
4263  break;
4264 
4265  case ERROR_EXPECT_SWITCH_SCOPE:
4266  dump += OS_TEXT(" EXPECT_SWITCH_SCOPE");
4267  break;
4268 
4269  case ERROR_EXPECT_LOOP_SCOPE:
4270  dump += OS_TEXT(" ERROR_EXPECT_LOOP_SCOPE");
4271  break;
4272 
4273  case ERROR_FINISH_BINARY_OP:
4274  dump += OS_TEXT(" FINISH_BINARY_OP");
4275  break;
4276 
4277  case ERROR_FINISH_UNARY_OP:
4278  dump += OS_TEXT(" FINISH_UNARY_OP");
4279  break;
4280  }
4281  allocator->getGlobal(OS_TEXT("CompilerException"));
4282  allocator->pushGlobals();
4283  allocator->pushString(dump);
4284  allocator->pushNumber(error);
4285  allocator->callFT(2, 1);
4286  if(error_token){
4287  if(!error_token->text_data->filename.isEmpty()){
4288  allocator->pushString(error_token->text_data->filename);
4289  }else{
4290  allocator->pushString(OS_TEXT("{{eval}}"));
4291  }
4292  allocator->setProperty(-2, OS_TEXT("file"), false);
4293 
4294  allocator->pushNumber(error_token->line+1);
4295  allocator->setProperty(-2, OS_TEXT("line"), false);
4296 
4297  allocator->pushNumber(error_token->pos+1);
4298  allocator->setProperty(-2, OS_TEXT("pos"), false);
4299 
4300  allocator->pushString(error_token->str);
4301  allocator->setProperty(-2, OS_TEXT("token"), false);
4302 
4303  allocator->pushString(error_token->text_data->lines[error_token->line]);
4304  allocator->setProperty(-2, OS_TEXT("lineString"), false);
4305  }else if(tokenizer->isError()){
4306  if(!tokenizer->getFilename().isEmpty()){
4307  allocator->pushString(tokenizer->getFilename());
4308  }else{
4309  allocator->pushString(OS_TEXT("{{eval}}"));
4310  }
4311  allocator->setProperty(-2, OS_TEXT("file"), false);
4312 
4313  allocator->pushNumber(tokenizer->getErrorLine()+1);
4314  allocator->setProperty(-2, OS_TEXT("line"), false);
4315 
4316  allocator->pushNumber(tokenizer->getErrorPos()+1);
4317  allocator->setProperty(-2, OS_TEXT("pos"), false);
4318 
4319  allocator->pushNull();
4320  allocator->setProperty(-2, OS_TEXT("token"), false);
4321 
4322  allocator->pushString(tokenizer->getLineString(tokenizer->getErrorLine()));
4323  allocator->setProperty(-2, OS_TEXT("lineString"), false);
4324  }
4325  allocator->setException();
4326  allocator->pushNull();
4327  return false;
4328 }

4448 OS::Core::Compiler::OpcodeLevel OS::Core::Compiler::getOpcodeLevel(ExpressionType exp_type)
4449 {
4450  switch(exp_type){
4451  case EXP_TYPE_ASSIGN: // =
4452  case EXP_TYPE_BIT_AND_ASSIGN: // &=
4453  case EXP_TYPE_BIT_OR_ASSIGN: // |=
4454  case EXP_TYPE_BIT_XOR_ASSIGN: // ^=
4455  case EXP_TYPE_BIT_NOT_ASSIGN: // ~=
4456  case EXP_TYPE_ADD_ASSIGN: // +=
4457  case EXP_TYPE_SUB_ASSIGN: // -=
4458  case EXP_TYPE_MUL_ASSIGN: // *=
4459  case EXP_TYPE_DIV_ASSIGN: // /=
4460  case EXP_TYPE_MOD_ASSIGN: // %=
4461  case EXP_TYPE_LSHIFT_ASSIGN: // <<=
4462  case EXP_TYPE_RSHIFT_ASSIGN: // >>=
4463  case EXP_TYPE_POW_ASSIGN: // **=
4464  return OP_LEVEL_1;
4465 
4466  case EXP_TYPE_PARAMS: // ,
4467  return OP_LEVEL_1_1;
4468 
4469  case EXP_TYPE_QUESTION: // ? :
4470  return OP_LEVEL_2;
4471 
4472  case EXP_TYPE_LOGIC_OR: // ||
4473  return OP_LEVEL_3;
4474 
4475  case EXP_TYPE_LOGIC_AND: // &&
4476  return OP_LEVEL_4;
4477 
4478  case EXP_TYPE_CONCAT: // ..
4479  return OP_LEVEL_5;
4480 
4481  case EXP_TYPE_LOGIC_PTR_EQ: // ===
4482  case EXP_TYPE_LOGIC_PTR_NE: // !==
4483  case EXP_TYPE_LOGIC_EQ: // ==
4484  case EXP_TYPE_LOGIC_NE: // !=
4485  return OP_LEVEL_6;
4486 
4487  case EXP_TYPE_LOGIC_GE: // >=
4488  case EXP_TYPE_LOGIC_LE: // <=
4489  case EXP_TYPE_LOGIC_GREATER: // >
4490  case EXP_TYPE_LOGIC_LESS: // <
4491  case EXP_TYPE_COMPARE: // <=>
4492  return OP_LEVEL_7;
4493 
4494  case EXP_TYPE_BIT_OR: // |
4495  return OP_LEVEL_8;
4496 
4497  case EXP_TYPE_BIT_AND: // &
4498  case EXP_TYPE_BIT_XOR: // ^
4499  return OP_LEVEL_9;
4500 
4501  case EXP_TYPE_LSHIFT: // <<
4502  case EXP_TYPE_RSHIFT: // >>
4503  return OP_LEVEL_10;
4504 
4505  case EXP_TYPE_ADD: // +
4506  case EXP_TYPE_SUB: // -
4507  return OP_LEVEL_11;
4508 
4509  case EXP_TYPE_MUL: // *
4510  case EXP_TYPE_DIV: // /
4511  case EXP_TYPE_MOD: // %
4512  return OP_LEVEL_12;
4513 
4514  case EXP_TYPE_POW: // **
4515  case EXP_TYPE_IN:
4516  case EXP_TYPE_IS:
4517  case EXP_TYPE_AS:
4518  return OP_LEVEL_13;
4519 
4520  case EXP_TYPE_PRE_INC: // ++
4521  case EXP_TYPE_PRE_DEC: // --
4522  case EXP_TYPE_POST_INC: // ++
4523  case EXP_TYPE_POST_DEC: // --
4524  return OP_LEVEL_14;
4525 
4526  case EXP_TYPE_LOGIC_BOOL: // !!
4527  case EXP_TYPE_LOGIC_NOT: // !
4528  case EXP_TYPE_PLUS: // +
4529  case EXP_TYPE_MINUS: // -
4530  case EXP_TYPE_LENGTH: // #
4531  case EXP_TYPE_BIT_NOT: // ~
4532  return OP_LEVEL_15;
4533 
4534  case EXP_TYPE_INDIRECT:
4535  case EXP_TYPE_BEFORE_INJECT_VAR:
4536  case EXP_TYPE_AFTER_INJECT_VAR:
4537  return OP_LEVEL_16;
4538  }
4539  return OP_LEVEL_0;
4540 }

4548 OS::Core::Tokenizer::TokenData * OS::Core::Compiler::readToken()
4549 {
4550  if(isError()){
4551  return NULL;
4552  }
4553  if(next_token_index < tokenizer->getNumTokens()){
4554  return recent_token = tokenizer->getToken(next_token_index++);
4555  }
4556  return recent_token = NULL;
4557 }
4558 
4559 OS::Core::Tokenizer::TokenData * OS::Core::Compiler::setNextTokenIndex(int i)
4560 {
4561  OS_ASSERT(tokenizer && i >= 0 && i <= tokenizer->getNumTokens());
4562  next_token_index = i;
4563  return recent_token = next_token_index > 0 ? tokenizer->getToken(next_token_index-1) : NULL;
4564 }
4565 
4566 OS::Core::Tokenizer::TokenData * OS::Core::Compiler::setNextToken(TokenData * token)
4567 {
4568  OS_ASSERT(tokenizer);
4569  int i, count = tokenizer->getNumTokens();
4570  for(i = next_token_index - 1; i >= 0; i--){
4571  if(tokenizer->getToken(i) == token)
4572  break;
4573  }
4574  if(i < 0){
4575  for(i = next_token_index; i < count; i++){
4576  if(tokenizer->getToken(i) == token)
4577  break;
4578  }
4579  }
4580  if(i >= 0 && i < count){
4581  next_token_index = i;
4582  return recent_token = next_token_index > 0 ? tokenizer->getToken(next_token_index-1) : NULL;
4583  }
4584  OS_ASSERT(false);
4585  return NULL;
4586 }

4588 OS::Core::Tokenizer::TokenData * OS::Core::Compiler::putNextTokenType(TokenType token_type)
4589 {
4590  if(token_type == Tokenizer::CODE_SEPARATOR && recent_token && recent_token->type == token_type){
4591  return ungetToken();
4592  }
4593  TokenData * token = recent_token;
4594  if(readToken()){
4595  if(recent_token->type == token_type){
4596  return ungetToken();
4597  }
4598  ungetToken();
4599  token = recent_token;
4600  }
4601  if(!token){
4602  if(next_token_index > 0){
4603  token = tokenizer->getToken(next_token_index-1);
4604  }
4605  }
4606  if(token){
4607  token = new (malloc(sizeof(TokenData) OS_DBG_FILEPOS)) TokenData(token->text_data, String(allocator), token_type, token->line, token->pos);
4608  }else{
4609  token = new (malloc(sizeof(TokenData) OS_DBG_FILEPOS)) TokenData(tokenizer->getTextData(), String(allocator), token_type, 0, 0);
4610  }
4611  tokenizer->insertToken(next_token_index, token OS_DBG_FILEPOS);
4612  return token;
4613 }
4614 
4615 OS::Core::Tokenizer::TokenData * OS::Core::Compiler::ungetToken()
4616 {
4617  return setNextTokenIndex(next_token_index-1);
4618 }

4620 bool OS::Core::Compiler::isNextTokens(TokenType * list, int count)
4621 {
4622  bool ok = true;
4623  int save_next_token_index = next_token_index;
4624  for(int i = 0; i < count; i++){
4625  if(!readToken() || !recent_token->isTypeOf(list[i])){
4626  ok = false;
4627  break;
4628  }
4629  }
4630  setNextTokenIndex(save_next_token_index);
4631  return ok;
4632 }

4694 OS::Core::Compiler::Expression * OS::Core::Compiler::expectExpressionValues(Expression * exp, int ret_values, bool auto_no_values)
4695 {
4696  if(exp->ret_values == ret_values || ret_values < 0){
4697  return exp;
4698  }
4699  switch(exp->type){
4700  case EXP_TYPE_CALL:
4701  case EXP_TYPE_CALL_AUTO_PARAM:
4702  case EXP_TYPE_CALL_DIM:
4703  case EXP_TYPE_CALL_METHOD:
4704  case EXP_TYPE_GET_PROPERTY:
4705  case EXP_TYPE_GET_THIS_PROPERTY_BY_STRING:
4706  case EXP_TYPE_GET_PROPERTY_BY_LOCALS:
4707  case EXP_TYPE_GET_PROPERTY_BY_LOCAL_AND_NUMBER:
4708  case EXP_TYPE_GET_PROPERTY_AUTO_CREATE:
4709  case EXP_TYPE_INDIRECT:
4710  case EXP_TYPE_TAIL_CALL: // ret values are not used for tail call
4711  case EXP_TYPE_TAIL_CALL_METHOD: // ret values are not used for tail call
4712  case EXP_TYPE_BREAK:
4713  case EXP_TYPE_CONTINUE:
4714  case EXP_TYPE_THROW:
4715  exp->ret_values = ret_values;
4716  return exp;
4717 
4718  case EXP_TYPE_BIT_AND_ASSIGN: // &=
4719  case EXP_TYPE_BIT_OR_ASSIGN: // |=
4720  case EXP_TYPE_BIT_XOR_ASSIGN: // ^=
4721  case EXP_TYPE_BIT_NOT_ASSIGN: // ~=
4722  case EXP_TYPE_ADD_ASSIGN: // +=
4723  case EXP_TYPE_SUB_ASSIGN: // -=
4724  case EXP_TYPE_MUL_ASSIGN: // *=
4725  case EXP_TYPE_DIV_ASSIGN: // /=
4726  case EXP_TYPE_MOD_ASSIGN: // %=
4727  case EXP_TYPE_LSHIFT_ASSIGN: // <<=
4728  case EXP_TYPE_RSHIFT_ASSIGN: // >>=
4729  case EXP_TYPE_POW_ASSIGN: // **=
4730  OS_ASSERT(exp->list.count == 1);
4731  // no break
4732 
4733  case EXP_TYPE_CODE_LIST:
4734  if(exp->list.count > 0){
4735  Expression * last_exp = exp->list.lastElement();
4736  exp->list.lastElement() = last_exp = expectExpressionValues(last_exp, ret_values, auto_no_values);
4737  exp->ret_values = last_exp->ret_values;
4738  return exp;
4739  }
4740  break;
4741 
4742  case EXP_TYPE_RETURN:
4743  exp = new (malloc(sizeof(Expression) OS_DBG_FILEPOS)) Expression(EXP_TYPE_CODE_LIST, exp->token, exp OS_DBG_FILEPOS);
4744  exp->ret_values = ret_values;
4745  return exp;
4746 
4747  case EXP_TYPE_PARAMS:
4748  if(exp->ret_values > ret_values){
4749  for(int i = exp->list.count-1; exp->ret_values > ret_values && i >= 0; i--){
4750  Expression * param_exp = exp->list[i];
4751  if(param_exp->type == EXP_TYPE_PARAMS){
4752  break;
4753  }
4754  OS_ASSERT(param_exp->type != EXP_TYPE_PARAMS);
4755  OS_ASSERT(param_exp->type != EXP_TYPE_RETURN);
4756  OS_ASSERT(param_exp->type != EXP_TYPE_CODE_LIST);
4757  if(param_exp->isConstValue()){
4758  exp->list.removeIndex(i);
4759  exp->ret_values--;
4760  allocator->deleteObj(param_exp);
4761  continue;
4762  }
4763  switch(param_exp->type){
4764  case EXP_TYPE_CALL:
4765  case EXP_TYPE_CALL_AUTO_PARAM:
4766  case EXP_TYPE_CALL_DIM:
4767  case EXP_TYPE_CALL_METHOD:
4768  case EXP_TYPE_GET_PROPERTY:
4769  case EXP_TYPE_GET_THIS_PROPERTY_BY_STRING:
4770  case EXP_TYPE_GET_PROPERTY_BY_LOCALS:
4771  case EXP_TYPE_GET_PROPERTY_BY_LOCAL_AND_NUMBER:
4772  case EXP_TYPE_GET_PROPERTY_AUTO_CREATE:
4773  case EXP_TYPE_INDIRECT:
4774  case EXP_TYPE_BREAK:
4775  case EXP_TYPE_CONTINUE:
4776  if(exp->ret_values <= param_exp->ret_values){
4777  param_exp->ret_values -= exp->ret_values;
4778  exp->ret_values = 0;
4779  }else{
4780  exp->ret_values -= param_exp->ret_values;
4781  param_exp->ret_values = 0;
4782  }
4783  continue;
4784  }
4785  break;
4786  }
4787  }
4788  break;
4789 
4790  case EXP_TYPE_PRE_INC:
4791  case EXP_TYPE_PRE_DEC:
4792  case EXP_TYPE_POST_INC:
4793  case EXP_TYPE_POST_DEC:
4794  OS_ASSERT(exp->ret_values == 1);
4795  if(!ret_values){
4796  exp->ret_values = 0;
4797  return exp;
4798  }
4799  break;
4800 
4801  case EXP_TYPE_SET_LOCAL_VAR:
4802  if(ret_values == 1){
4803  exp->type = EXP_TYPE_SET_LOCAL_VAR_NO_POP;
4804  exp->ret_values = 1;
4805  return exp;
4806  }
4807  break;
4808 
4809  case EXP_TYPE_SET_UPVALUE:
4810  if(ret_values == 1){
4811  exp->type = EXP_TYPE_SET_UPVALUE_NO_POP;
4812  exp->ret_values = 1;
4813  return exp;
4814  }
4815  break;
4816 
4817  case EXP_TYPE_SET_ENV_VAR:
4818  if(ret_values == 1){
4819  exp->type = EXP_TYPE_SET_ENV_VAR_NO_POP;
4820  exp->ret_values = 1;
4821  return exp;
4822  }
4823  break;
4824 
4825  case EXP_TYPE_SET_PROPERTY:
4826  OS_ASSERT(!exp->ret_values);
4827  exp->type = EXP_TYPE_SET_PROPERTY_NO_POP;
4828  exp->ret_values = 1;
4829  break;
4830 
4831  case EXP_TYPE_SET_DIM:
4832  OS_ASSERT(!exp->ret_values && ret_values >= 1);
4833  exp->type = EXP_TYPE_SET_DIM_NO_POP;
4834  exp->ret_values = 1;
4835  break;
4836  }
4837  while(exp->ret_values > ret_values){
4838  int new_ret_values = exp->ret_values-1;
4839  exp = new (malloc(sizeof(Expression) OS_DBG_FILEPOS)) Expression(EXP_TYPE_POP_VALUE, exp->token, exp OS_DBG_FILEPOS);
4840  exp->ret_values = new_ret_values;
4841  }
4842  if(exp->ret_values < ret_values){
4843  if(exp->type != EXP_TYPE_PARAMS){
4844  exp = new (malloc(sizeof(Expression) OS_DBG_FILEPOS)) Expression(EXP_TYPE_PARAMS, exp->token, exp OS_DBG_FILEPOS);
4845  exp->ret_values = exp->list[0]->ret_values;
4846  }
4847  while(exp->ret_values < ret_values){
4848  if(auto_no_values && exp->ret_values+1 == ret_values){
4849  break;
4850  }
4851  Expression * null_exp = new (malloc(sizeof(Expression) OS_DBG_FILEPOS)) Expression(EXP_TYPE_CONST_NULL, exp->token);
4852  null_exp->ret_values = 1;
4853  exp->list.add(null_exp OS_DBG_FILEPOS);
4854  exp->ret_values++;
4855  }
4856  }
4857  return exp;
4858 }
4859 
4860 OS::Core::Compiler::Expression * OS::Core::Compiler::newSingleValueExpression(Expression * exp)
4861 {
4862  exp = expectExpressionValues(exp, 1);
4863  switch(exp->type){
4864  case EXP_TYPE_CALL:
4865  case EXP_TYPE_CALL_AUTO_PARAM:
4866  case EXP_TYPE_CALL_DIM:
4867  case EXP_TYPE_CALL_METHOD:
4868  case EXP_TYPE_GET_PROPERTY:
4869  case EXP_TYPE_GET_THIS_PROPERTY_BY_STRING:
4870  case EXP_TYPE_GET_PROPERTY_BY_LOCALS:
4871  case EXP_TYPE_GET_PROPERTY_BY_LOCAL_AND_NUMBER:
4872  case EXP_TYPE_GET_PROPERTY_AUTO_CREATE:
4873  case EXP_TYPE_INDIRECT:
4874  {
4875  exp = new (malloc(sizeof(Expression) OS_DBG_FILEPOS)) Expression(EXP_TYPE_VALUE, exp->token, exp OS_DBG_FILEPOS);
4876  exp->ret_values = 1;
4877  break;
4878  }
4879  }
4880  return exp;
4881 }

4883 OS::Core::Compiler::Expression * OS::Core::Compiler::newExpressionFromList(ExpressionList& list, int ret_values, bool auto_no_values)
4884 {
4885  Expression * exp;
4886  if(list.count == 1){
4887  exp = list[0];
4888  list.removeIndex(0);
4889  }else if(list.count == 0){
4890  TokenData * cur_token = ungetToken();
4891  readToken();
4892  exp = new (malloc(sizeof(Expression) OS_DBG_FILEPOS)) Expression(EXP_TYPE_CODE_LIST, cur_token);
4893  }else{
4894  int i;
4895  for(i = 0; i < list.count-1; i++){
4896  OS_ASSERT(list[i]->type != EXP_TYPE_CODE_LIST);
4897  list[i] = expectExpressionValues(list[i], 0);
4898  }
4899  exp = new (malloc(sizeof(Expression) OS_DBG_FILEPOS)) Expression(EXP_TYPE_CODE_LIST, list[0]->token);
4900  exp->list.swap(list);
4901  exp->ret_values = exp->list[exp->list.count-1]->ret_values;
4902  }
4903  return expectExpressionValues(exp, ret_values, auto_no_values);
4904 }
4905 
4906 OS::Core::Compiler::Expression * OS::Core::Compiler::postCompilePass2(Scope * scope, Expression * exp)
4907 {
4908 #ifdef OS_DEBUG
4909  allocator->checkNativeStackUsage(OS_TEXT("OS::Core::Compiler::postCompilePass2"));
4910 #endif
4911  if(isError()){
4912  return exp;
4913  }
4914  switch(exp->type){
4915  case EXP_TYPE_FUNCTION:
4916  {
4917  Scope * new_scope = dynamic_cast<Scope*>(exp);
4918  OS_ASSERT(new_scope); // && (new_scope->parent == scope || (!new_scope->parent && new_scope->type == EXP_TYPE_FUNCTION)));
4919  if(new_scope != scope){
4920  new_scope->func_index = scope->function->num_local_funcs++;
4921  new_scope->func_depth = scope->function->func_depth + 1;
4922  }
4923  scope = new_scope;
4924  OS_ASSERT(prog_functions.indexOf(scope) < 0);
4925  scope->prog_func_index = prog_functions.count;
4926  allocator->vectorAddItem(prog_functions, scope OS_DBG_FILEPOS);
4927  break;
4928  }
4929 
4930  case EXP_TYPE_SCOPE:
4931  case EXP_TYPE_LOOP_SCOPE:
4932  case EXP_TYPE_FOR_LOOP_SCOPE:
4933  case EXP_TYPE_SWITCH_SCOPE:
4934  {
4935  Scope * new_scope = dynamic_cast<Scope*>(exp);
4936  OS_ASSERT(new_scope); // && (new_scope->parent == scope || (!new_scope->parent && new_scope->type == EXP_TYPE_FUNCTION)));
4937  scope = new_scope;
4938  break;
4939  }
4940 
4941  case EXP_TYPE_DEBUG_LOCALS:
4942  if(exp->list.count == 0){
4943  Expression * obj_exp = new (malloc(sizeof(Expression) OS_DBG_FILEPOS)) Expression(EXP_TYPE_OBJECT, exp->token);
4944 
4945  Vector<String> vars;
4946 
4947  // skip std vars
4948  allocator->vectorAddItem(vars, allocator->core->strings->var_func OS_DBG_FILEPOS);
4949  allocator->vectorAddItem(vars, allocator->core->strings->var_this OS_DBG_FILEPOS);
4950  allocator->vectorAddItem(vars, allocator->core->strings->var_env OS_DBG_FILEPOS);
4951  allocator->vectorAddItem(vars, allocator->core->strings->var_globals OS_DBG_FILEPOS);
4952 
4953  Scope * start_scope = scope;
4954  for(; scope; scope = scope->parent){
4955  for(int i = scope->locals.count-1; i >= 0; i--){
4956  const Scope::LocalVar& local_var = scope->locals[i];
4957  if(local_var.name.toChar()[0] == OS_TEXT('#')){
4958  continue;
4959  }
4960  bool found = false;
4961  for(int j = 0; j < vars.count; j++){
4962  if(vars[j] == local_var.name){
4963  found = true;
4964  break;
4965  }
4966  }
4967  if(found){
4968  continue;
4969  }
4970  allocator->vectorAddItem(vars, local_var.name OS_DBG_FILEPOS);
4971 
4972  TokenData * name_token = new (malloc(sizeof(TokenData) OS_DBG_FILEPOS)) TokenData(tokenizer->getTextData(), local_var.name,
4973  Tokenizer::NAME, exp->token->line, exp->token->pos);
4974 
4975  Expression * var_exp = new (malloc(sizeof(Expression) OS_DBG_FILEPOS)) Expression(EXP_TYPE_GET_LOCAL_VAR, name_token);
4976  OS_ASSERT(scope->function);
4977  var_exp->active_locals = scope->function->num_locals;
4978  var_exp->ret_values = 1;
4979  found = findLocalVar(var_exp->local_var, start_scope, local_var.name, start_scope->function->num_locals, true);
4980  OS_ASSERT(found); // && var_exp->local_var.index == local_var.index);
4981  if(start_scope->function->max_up_count < var_exp->local_var.up_count){
4982  start_scope->function->max_up_count = var_exp->local_var.up_count;
4983  }
4984 
4985  Expression * obj_item_exp = new (malloc(sizeof(Expression) OS_DBG_FILEPOS)) Expression(EXP_TYPE_OBJECT_SET_BY_NAME, name_token, var_exp OS_DBG_FILEPOS);
4986  allocator->vectorInsertAtIndex(obj_exp->list, 0, obj_item_exp OS_DBG_FILEPOS);
4987 
4988  name_token->release();
4989  }
4990  }
4991  allocator->vectorClear(vars);
4992  obj_exp->ret_values = 1;
4993 
4994  scope = start_scope;
4995  exp->list.add(obj_exp OS_DBG_FILEPOS);
4996  }
4997  break;
4998 
4999  case EXP_TYPE_PARAMS:
5000  {
5001  for(int i = exp->list.count-1; i >= 0; i--){
5002  Expression * sub_exp = postCompilePass2(scope, exp->list[i]);
5003  if(sub_exp->type == EXP_TYPE_PARAMS){
5004  // OS_ASSERT(false);
5005  ExpressionList list(allocator);
5006  int j;
5007  for(j = 0; j < i; j++){
5008  list.add(exp->list[j] OS_DBG_FILEPOS);
5009  }
5010  for(j = 0; j < sub_exp->list.count; j++){
5011  list.add(sub_exp->list[j] OS_DBG_FILEPOS);
5012  }
5013  for(j = i+1; j < exp->list.count; j++){
5014  list.add(exp->list[j] OS_DBG_FILEPOS);
5015  }
5016  exp->ret_values += sub_exp->ret_values;
5017  list.swap(exp->list);
5018  allocator->vectorClear(list);
5019  allocator->vectorClear(sub_exp->list);
5020  allocator->deleteObj(sub_exp);
5021  }else{
5022  exp->list[i] = sub_exp;
5023  }
5024  }
5025  return exp;
5026  }
5027 
5028  case EXP_TYPE_POST_INC:
5029  case EXP_TYPE_POST_DEC:
5030  case EXP_TYPE_PRE_INC:
5031  case EXP_TYPE_PRE_DEC:
5032  OS_ASSERT(exp->list.count == 1);
5033  break;
5034 
5035  case EXP_TYPE_NAME:
5036  if(findLocalVar(exp->local_var, scope, exp->token->str, exp->active_locals, true)){
5037  exp->type = EXP_TYPE_GET_LOCAL_VAR;
5038  if(scope->function->max_up_count < exp->local_var.up_count){
5039  scope->function->max_up_count = exp->local_var.up_count;
5040  }
5041  }else{
5042  exp->type = EXP_TYPE_GET_ENV_VAR;
5043  }
5044  break;
5045 
5046  case EXP_TYPE_RETURN:
5047 #ifdef OS_TAIL_CALL_ENABLED
5048  if(exp->list.count == 1){
5049  Expression * sub_exp = exp->list[0] = postCompilePass2(scope, exp->list[0]);
5050  switch(sub_exp->type){
5051  case EXP_TYPE_CALL:
5052  case EXP_TYPE_CALL_AUTO_PARAM:
5053  sub_exp->type = EXP_TYPE_TAIL_CALL;
5054  allocator->vectorClear(exp->list);
5055  allocator->deleteObj(exp);
5056  return sub_exp;
5057 
5058  case EXP_TYPE_CALL_METHOD:
5059  sub_exp->type = EXP_TYPE_TAIL_CALL_METHOD;
5060  allocator->vectorClear(exp->list);
5061  allocator->deleteObj(exp);
5062  return sub_exp;
5063  }
5064  return exp;
5065  }
5066 #endif
5067  break;
5068 
5069  case EXP_TYPE_CALL:
5070  case EXP_TYPE_CALL_AUTO_PARAM:
5071  {
5072  OS_ASSERT(exp->list.count == 2);
5073  exp->list[0] = postCompilePass2(scope, exp->list[0]);
5074  exp->list[1] = postCompilePass2(scope, exp->list[1]);
5075  Expression * left_exp = exp->list[0];
5076  Expression * right_exp = exp->list[1];
5077  if(left_exp->type == EXP_TYPE_GET_PROPERTY){
5078  OS_ASSERT(left_exp->list.count == 2);
5079  OS_ASSERT(right_exp->type == EXP_TYPE_PARAMS);
5080  allocator->vectorInsertAtIndex(right_exp->list, 0, left_exp->list[1] OS_DBG_FILEPOS);
5081  right_exp->ret_values += left_exp->list[1]->ret_values;
5082  left_exp->list[1] = right_exp;
5083  left_exp->type = EXP_TYPE_CALL_METHOD;
5084  left_exp->ret_values = exp->ret_values;
5085  allocator->vectorClear(exp->list);
5086  allocator->deleteObj(exp);
5087  return left_exp;
5088  }
5089  if(left_exp->type == EXP_TYPE_GET_ENV_VAR){
5090  OS_ASSERT(left_exp->list.count == 0);
5091  OS_ASSERT(right_exp->type == EXP_TYPE_PARAMS);
5092  left_exp->type = EXP_TYPE_CONST_STRING;
5093  allocator->vectorInsertAtIndex(right_exp->list, 0, left_exp OS_DBG_FILEPOS);
5094  right_exp->ret_values++;
5095 
5096  TokenData * name_token = new (malloc(sizeof(TokenData) OS_DBG_FILEPOS)) TokenData(tokenizer->getTextData(),
5097  allocator->core->strings->var_env,
5098  Tokenizer::NAME, left_exp->token->line, left_exp->token->pos);
5099 
5100  left_exp = new (malloc(sizeof(Expression) OS_DBG_FILEPOS)) Expression(EXP_TYPE_GET_LOCAL_VAR, name_token);
5101  left_exp->ret_values = 1;
5102  if(!findLocalVar(left_exp->local_var, scope, name_token->str, scope->function->num_params + POST_VAR_ENV+1, true)){
5103  OS_ASSERT(false);
5104  };
5105  if(scope->function->max_up_count < left_exp->local_var.up_count){
5106  scope->function->max_up_count = left_exp->local_var.up_count;
5107  }
5108  exp->list[0] = left_exp;
5109 
5110  name_token->release();
5111 
5112  exp->type = EXP_TYPE_CALL_METHOD;
5113  return exp;
5114  }

5119  case EXP_TYPE_SET_DIM_NO_POP:

5276  break;
5277  }

5280  exp->list[i] = postCompilePass2(scope, exp->list[i]);
5281  }
5282  switch(exp->type){
5283  case EXP_TYPE_CONST_NUMBER:
5284  exp->local_var.type = CVT_NUMBER;
5285  break;
5286 
5287  case EXP_TYPE_GET_LOCAL_VAR:
5288  exp->local_var.type = scope->getLocalVar(exp->local_var).type;
5289  break;
5290 
5291  case EXP_TYPE_SET_LOCAL_VAR:
5292  {
5293  OS_ASSERT(exp->list.count == 1);
5294  Expression * exp2 = exp->list[0];
5295  if(exp->local_var.type != CVT_DYNAMIC){
5296  ECompiledValueType old_type = exp->local_var.type;
5297  if(exp2->local_var.type == CVT_NUMBER){
5298  exp->local_var.type = CVT_NUMBER;
5299  }else{
5300  exp->local_var.type = CVT_DYNAMIC;
5301  }
5302  if(old_type != exp->local_var.type){
5303  scope->getLocalVar(exp->local_var).type = exp->local_var.type;
5304  }
5305  }
5306  break;
5307  }
5308 
5309  case EXP_TYPE_ASSIGN:
5310  OS_ASSERT(false);
5311  OS_ASSERT(exp->list.count == 2);
5312  if(exp->list[0]->type == EXP_TYPE_NAME){
5313  Expression * left_exp = exp->list[0];
5314  Expression * right_exp = exp->list[1];
5315  if(left_exp->local_var.type != CVT_DYNAMIC){
5316  if(right_exp->local_var.type == CVT_NUMBER){
5317  left_exp->local_var.type = CVT_NUMBER;
5318  }else{
5319  left_exp->local_var.type = CVT_DYNAMIC;
5320  }
5321  }
5322  }
5323  break;
5324 
5325  case EXP_TYPE_BIT_AND:
5326  case EXP_TYPE_BIT_OR:
5327  case EXP_TYPE_BIT_XOR:
5328  case EXP_TYPE_COMPARE: // <=>
5329  case EXP_TYPE_ADD: // +
5330  case EXP_TYPE_SUB: // -
5331  case EXP_TYPE_MUL: // *
5332  case EXP_TYPE_DIV: // /
5333  case EXP_TYPE_MOD: // %
5334  case EXP_TYPE_LSHIFT: // <<
5335  case EXP_TYPE_RSHIFT: // >>
5336  case EXP_TYPE_POW: // **
5337  {
5338  OS_ASSERT(exp->list.count == 2);
5339  Expression * left_exp = exp->list[0];
5340  Expression * right_exp = exp->list[1];
5341  if(left_exp->local_var.type == CVT_NUMBER && right_exp->local_var.type == CVT_NUMBER){
5342  exp->local_var.type = CVT_NUMBER;
5343  }else{
5344  exp->local_var.type = CVT_DYNAMIC;
5345  }
5346  break;
5347  }
5348  }
5349  return exp;
5350 }

5352 OS::Core::Compiler::Expression * OS::Core::Compiler::postCompileFixValueType(Scope * scope, Expression * exp)
5353 {
5354  if(isError()){
5355  return exp;
5356  }
5357  switch(exp->type){
5358  case EXP_TYPE_FUNCTION:
5359  {
5360  Scope * new_scope = dynamic_cast<Scope*>(exp);
5361  OS_ASSERT(new_scope); // && (new_scope->parent == scope || (!new_scope->parent && new_scope->type == EXP_TYPE_FUNCTION)));
5362  if(new_scope != scope){
5363  new_scope->func_index = scope->function->num_local_funcs++;
5364  new_scope->func_depth = scope->function->func_depth + 1;
5365  }
5366  scope = new_scope;
5367  break;
5368  }
5369 
5370  case EXP_TYPE_SCOPE:
5371  case EXP_TYPE_LOOP_SCOPE:
5372  case EXP_TYPE_FOR_LOOP_SCOPE:
5373  case EXP_TYPE_SWITCH_SCOPE:
5374  {
5375  Scope * new_scope = dynamic_cast<Scope*>(exp);
5376  OS_ASSERT(new_scope); // && (new_scope->parent == scope || (!new_scope->parent && new_scope->type == EXP_TYPE_FUNCTION)));
5377  scope = new_scope;
5378  break;
5379  }
5380  }
5381  for(int i = 0; i < exp->list.count; i++){
5382  exp->list[i] = postCompileFixValueType(scope, exp->list[i]);
5383  }
5384  switch(exp->type){
5385  case EXP_TYPE_GET_LOCAL_VAR:
5386  if(exp->local_var.type == CVT_NUMBER){
5387  exp->local_var.type = scope->getLocalVar(exp->local_var).type;
5388  }
5389  break;
5390 
5391  case EXP_TYPE_SET_LOCAL_VAR:
5392  if(exp->local_var.type == CVT_NUMBER){
5393  OS_ASSERT(exp->list.count == 1);
5394  Expression * exp2 = exp->list[0];
5395  ECompiledValueType old_type = exp->local_var.type;
5396  if(exp2->local_var.type == CVT_NUMBER){
5397  exp->local_var.type = CVT_NUMBER;
5398  }else{
5399  exp->local_var.type = CVT_DYNAMIC;
5400  }
5401  if(old_type != exp->local_var.type){
5402  scope->getLocalVar(exp->local_var).type = exp->local_var.type;
5403  }
5404  break;
5405  }
5406 
5407  case EXP_TYPE_BIT_AND:
5408  case EXP_TYPE_BIT_OR:
5409  case EXP_TYPE_BIT_XOR:
5410  case EXP_TYPE_COMPARE: // <=>
5411  case EXP_TYPE_ADD: // +
5412  case EXP_TYPE_SUB: // -
5413  case EXP_TYPE_MUL: // *
5414  case EXP_TYPE_DIV: // /
5415  case EXP_TYPE_MOD: // %
5416  case EXP_TYPE_LSHIFT: // <<
5417  case EXP_TYPE_RSHIFT: // >>
5418  case EXP_TYPE_POW: // **
5419  if(exp->local_var.type == CVT_NUMBER){
5420  OS_ASSERT(exp->list.count == 2);
5421  Expression * left_exp = exp->list[0];
5422  Expression * right_exp = exp->list[1];
5423  if(left_exp->local_var.type == CVT_NUMBER && right_exp->local_var.type == CVT_NUMBER){
5424  exp->local_var.type = CVT_NUMBER;
5425  }else{
5426  exp->local_var.type = CVT_DYNAMIC;
5427  }
5428  break;
5429  }
5430  }
5431  return exp;
5432 }

5435 {
5436  exp = postCompilePass2(scope, exp);
5437 #if 0
5438  return exp;
5439 #elif 1
5440  OS_ASSERT(scope->type == EXP_TYPE_FUNCTION);

5442  exp = postCompilePass3(scope, exp);
5443  exp = postCompileNewVM(scope, exp);

5447  return NULL;
5448  }
5449  return exp;
5450 #else

5454 #endif

5457 OS::Core::Compiler::Expression * OS::Core::Compiler::postCompilePass3(Scope * scope, Expression * exp)
5458 {
5459  struct Lib {
5460  static Expression * processList(Compiler * compiler, Scope * scope, Expression * exp)
5461  {
5462  for(int i = 0; i < exp->list.count && !compiler->isError(); i++){
5463  exp->list[i] = compiler->postCompilePass3(scope, exp->list[i]);
5464  }
5465  return exp;
5466  }
5467  };
5468  if(isError()){
5469  return exp;
5470  }
5471  switch(exp->type){
5472  case EXP_TYPE_FUNCTION:
5473  {
5474  Scope * new_scope = dynamic_cast<Scope*>(exp);
5475  OS_ASSERT(new_scope); // && (new_scope->parent == scope || (!new_scope->parent && new_scope->type == EXP_TYPE_FUNCTION)));
5476  scope = new_scope;
5477  break;
5478  }
5479 
5480  case EXP_TYPE_SCOPE:
5481  case EXP_TYPE_LOOP_SCOPE:
5482  case EXP_TYPE_FOR_LOOP_SCOPE:
5483  case EXP_TYPE_SWITCH_SCOPE:
5484  {
5485  Scope * new_scope = dynamic_cast<Scope*>(exp);
5486  OS_ASSERT(new_scope); // && (new_scope->parent == scope || (!new_scope->parent && new_scope->type == EXP_TYPE_FUNCTION)));
5487  scope = new_scope;
5488  break;
5489  }
5490 
5491  case EXP_TYPE_CALL:
5492  case EXP_TYPE_CALL_AUTO_PARAM:
5493  case EXP_TYPE_TAIL_CALL:
5494  {
5495  OS_ASSERT(exp->list.count == 2);
5496  Expression * exp_params = exp->list[1];
5497  OS_ASSERT(exp_params->type == EXP_TYPE_PARAMS);

5499  exp_this->ret_values = 1;
5500  allocator->vectorInsertAtIndex(exp_params->list, 0, exp_this OS_DBG_FILEPOS);
5501  exp_params->ret_values++;
5502  return Lib::processList(this, scope, exp);
5503  }
5504 
5505  case EXP_TYPE_GET_ENV_VAR:
5506  case EXP_TYPE_GET_ENV_VAR_AUTO_CREATE:

5508  exp->slots.b = cacheString(exp->token->str);
5509  break;
5510 
5511  case EXP_TYPE_SET_ENV_VAR:
5512  case EXP_TYPE_SET_ENV_VAR_NO_POP:
5513  OS_ASSERT(exp->list.count == 1);
5514  exp->slots.b = cacheString(exp->token->str);
5515  break;
5516

5534  break;

5539  break;

5543  exp->slots.b = cacheString(exp->token->str);
5544  break;
5545

5560  break;
5561

5563  OS_ASSERT(exp->list.count == 2);
5564  exp->slots.b = cacheString(allocator->core->strings->func_extends);
5565  break;
5566 
5567  case EXP_TYPE_IN:

5569  exp->slots.b = cacheString(allocator->core->strings->func_in);
5570  break;
5571

5576

5578  OS_ASSERT(exp->list.count == 2);
5579  exp->slots.b = cacheString(allocator->core->strings->func_as);
5580  break;
5581 
5582  case EXP_TYPE_CONST_NUMBER:
5583  OS_ASSERT(exp->list.count == 0);
5584  exp->slots.b = cacheNumber((OS_NUMBER)exp->token->getFloat());
5585  break;
5586 
5587  case EXP_TYPE_CONST_STRING:
5588  OS_ASSERT(exp->list.count == 0);
5589  exp->slots.b = cacheString(exp->token->str);
5590  break;
5591

5594  exp->slots.b = CONST_NULL;
5595  break;
5596 
5597  case EXP_TYPE_CONST_FALSE:
5598  OS_ASSERT(exp->list.count == 0);
5599  exp->slots.b = CONST_FALSE;
5600  break;
5601 
5602  case EXP_TYPE_CONST_TRUE:
5603  OS_ASSERT(exp->list.count == 0);
5604  exp->slots.b = CONST_TRUE;
5605  break;
5606 
5607  case EXP_TYPE_PRE_INC:
5608  case EXP_TYPE_PRE_DEC:
5609  case EXP_TYPE_POST_INC:
5610  case EXP_TYPE_POST_DEC:
5611  OS_ASSERT(exp->list.count == 1);
5612  exp->slots.b = cacheNumber((OS_NUMBER)1.0);
5613  break;
5614  }
5615  return Lib::processList(this, scope, exp);
5616 }
5617 OS::Core::Compiler::Expression * OS::Core::Compiler::postCompileNewVM(Scope * scope, Expression * exp)
5618 {
5619  struct Lib {
5620  static Expression * processList(Compiler * compiler, Scope * scope, Expression * exp)
5621  {
5622  for(int i = 0; i < exp->list.count && !compiler->isError(); i++){
5623  exp->list[i] = compiler->postCompileNewVM(scope, exp->list[i]);
5624  }
5625  return exp;
5626  }
5627 
5628  static bool allowOverrideOpcodeResult(Expression * exp)
5629  {
5630  switch(exp->type){
5631  case EXP_TYPE_FUNCTION:
5632  case EXP_TYPE_MOVE:
5633  case EXP_TYPE_CONST_NUMBER:
5634  case EXP_TYPE_CONST_STRING:
5635  case EXP_TYPE_CONST_NULL:
5636  case EXP_TYPE_CONST_FALSE:
5637  case EXP_TYPE_CONST_TRUE:
5638  case EXP_TYPE_CONCAT:
5639  case EXP_TYPE_BEFORE_INJECT_VAR:
5640  case EXP_TYPE_AFTER_INJECT_VAR:
5641  /*
5642  case EXP_TYPE_LOGIC_PTR_EQ:
5643  case EXP_TYPE_LOGIC_PTR_NE:
5644  case EXP_TYPE_LOGIC_EQ:
5645  case EXP_TYPE_LOGIC_NE:
5646  case EXP_TYPE_LOGIC_GE:
5647  case EXP_TYPE_LOGIC_LE:
5648  case EXP_TYPE_LOGIC_GREATER:
5649  case EXP_TYPE_LOGIC_LESS:
5650  */
5651  case EXP_TYPE_BIT_AND:
5652  case EXP_TYPE_BIT_OR:
5653  case EXP_TYPE_BIT_XOR:
5654  case EXP_TYPE_COMPARE: // <=>
5655  case EXP_TYPE_ADD: // +
5656  case EXP_TYPE_SUB: // -
5657  case EXP_TYPE_MUL: // *
5658  case EXP_TYPE_DIV: // /
5659  case EXP_TYPE_MOD: // %
5660  case EXP_TYPE_LSHIFT: // <<
5661  case EXP_TYPE_RSHIFT: // >>
5662  case EXP_TYPE_POW: // **
5663  case EXP_TYPE_GET_UPVALUE:
5664  case EXP_TYPE_GET_PROPERTY:
5665  return true;
5666  }
5667  return false;
5668  }
5669 
5670  static Expression * addXconst(Compiler * compiler, Expression * exp, Expression * xconst)
5671  {
5672  OS_ASSERT(!xconst || xconst->ret_values == 1);
5673  if(xconst){
5674  Expression * exp2 = new (compiler->malloc(sizeof(Expression) OS_DBG_FILEPOS)) Expression(EXP_TYPE_CODE_LIST, exp->token, xconst, exp OS_DBG_FILEPOS);
5675  exp2->ret_values = 1;
5676  return exp2;
5677  }
5678  return exp;
5679  }
5680  };
5681  if(isError()){
5682  return exp;
5683  }
5684  Expression * exp1, * exp2, * exp_xconst;
5685  int stack_pos, b, ret_slot;
5686  bool no_pop;
5687  ExpressionType exp_type;
5688  switch(exp->type){
5689  default:
5690  OS_ASSERT(false);
5691  break;
5692 
5693  case EXP_TYPE_DEBUGGER:
5694  break;
5695 
5696  case EXP_TYPE_FUNCTION:
5697  {
5698  Scope * new_scope = dynamic_cast<Scope*>(exp);
5699  OS_ASSERT(new_scope); // && (new_scope->parent == scope || (!new_scope->parent && new_scope->type == EXP_TYPE_FUNCTION)));
5700  scope = new_scope;
5701  scope->slots.a = scope->parent ? scope->parent->allocTempVar() : 0;
5702  scope->slots.b = scope->prog_func_index;
5703  break;
5704  }
5705 
5706  case EXP_TYPE_SCOPE:
5707  case EXP_TYPE_LOOP_SCOPE:
5708  case EXP_TYPE_FOR_LOOP_SCOPE:
5709  case EXP_TYPE_SWITCH_SCOPE:
5710  {
5711  Scope * new_scope = dynamic_cast<Scope*>(exp);
5712  OS_ASSERT(new_scope); // && (new_scope->parent == scope || (!new_scope->parent && new_scope->type == EXP_TYPE_FUNCTION)));
5713  scope = new_scope;
5714  break;
5715  }
5716 
5717  case EXP_TYPE_PARAMS:
5718  case EXP_TYPE_MOVE:
5719  case EXP_TYPE_NEW_LOCAL_VAR:
5720  case EXP_TYPE_BREAK:
5721  case EXP_TYPE_CONTINUE:
5722  case EXP_TYPE_NOP:
5723  case EXP_TYPE_TRY_CATCH:
5724  break;
5725 
5726  case EXP_TYPE_THROW:
5727  OS_ASSERT(exp->list.count == 1);
5728  stack_pos = scope->function->stack_cur_size;
5729  exp = Lib::processList(this, scope, exp);
5730  exp->slots.a = stack_pos;
5731  exp->slots.b = scope->function->stack_cur_size - stack_pos;
5732  exp->slots.c = 0;
5733  OS_ASSERT(exp->slots.b == 1);
5734  scope->function->stack_cur_size = stack_pos + exp->ret_values;
5735 #if 0 // don't allow optimization here
5736  exp1 = exp->list[0];
5737  if(exp1->type == EXP_TYPE_MOVE && exp1->slots.b >= 0){
5738  exp->slots.a = exp1->slots.b;
5739  exp1->type = EXP_TYPE_NOP;
5740  }
5741 #endif
5742  return exp;
5743 
5744  case EXP_TYPE_CODE_LIST:
5745  {
5746  stack_pos = scope->function->stack_cur_size;
5747  exp = Lib::processList(this, scope, exp);
5748  while(stack_pos + exp->ret_values > scope->function->stack_cur_size){
5749  scope->allocTempVar();
5750  }
5751  if(exp->ret_values > 0){
5752  OS_ASSERT(exp->list.count > 0);
5753  exp->slots.a = exp->list.lastElement()->slots.a;
5754  }
5755  return exp;
5756  }
5757 
5758  case EXP_TYPE_POP_VALUE:
5759  exp = Lib::processList(this, scope, exp);
5760  scope->popTempVar();
5761  return exp;
5762 
5763  case EXP_TYPE_VALUE:
5764  stack_pos = scope->function->stack_cur_size;
5765  exp = Lib::processList(this, scope, exp);
5766  OS_ASSERT(stack_pos+1 == scope->function->stack_cur_size);
5767  exp->slots.a = stack_pos;
5768  return exp;
5769 
5770  case EXP_TYPE_RETURN:
5771  stack_pos = scope->function->stack_cur_size;
5772  exp = Lib::processList(this, scope, exp);
5773  exp->slots.a = stack_pos;
5774  exp->slots.b = scope->function->stack_cur_size - stack_pos;
5775  exp->slots.c = 0;
5776  OS_ASSERT(exp->slots.b == exp->ret_values);
5777  scope->function->stack_cur_size = stack_pos;
5778  if(exp->slots.b == 1){
5779  OS_ASSERT(exp->list.count == 1);
5780  exp1 = exp->list[0];
5781  if(exp1->type == EXP_TYPE_MOVE && exp1->slots.b >= 0){ // scope->function->num_locals){
5782  exp->slots.a = exp1->slots.b;
5783  exp1->type = EXP_TYPE_NOP;
5784  }
5785  }
5786  return exp;
5787 
5788  case EXP_TYPE_CALL:
5789  case EXP_TYPE_CALL_AUTO_PARAM:
5790  case EXP_TYPE_TAIL_CALL:
5791  OS_ASSERT(exp->list.count == 2);
5792  OS_ASSERT(exp->list[1]->type == EXP_TYPE_PARAMS);
5793  exp1 = exp->list[0];
5794  if(exp1->type == EXP_TYPE_SUPER){
5795  exp1->type = EXP_TYPE_CONST_NULL;
5796  exp->type = EXP_TYPE_SUPER_CALL;
5797  }
5798  // no break
5799 
5800  case EXP_TYPE_CALL_METHOD:
5801  case EXP_TYPE_TAIL_CALL_METHOD:
5802  stack_pos = scope->function->stack_cur_size;
5803  exp = Lib::processList(this, scope, exp);
5804  exp->slots.a = stack_pos;
5805  exp->slots.b = scope->function->stack_cur_size - stack_pos;
5806  exp->slots.c = exp->ret_values;
5807  scope->function->stack_cur_size = stack_pos + exp->ret_values;
5808  if(scope->function->stack_size < scope->function->stack_cur_size){
5809  scope->function->stack_size = scope->function->stack_cur_size;
5810  }
5811  return exp;
5812 
5813  case EXP_TYPE_INIT_ITER:
5814  stack_pos = scope->function->stack_cur_size;
5815  exp = Lib::processList(this, scope, exp);
5816  exp->slots.a = stack_pos;
5817  OS_ASSERT(scope->function->stack_cur_size == stack_pos + exp->ret_values);
5818  return exp;
5819 
5820  case EXP_TYPE_IF:
5821  OS_ASSERT(exp->list.count == 2 || exp->list.count == 3);
5822  stack_pos = scope->function->stack_cur_size;
5823  exp->list[0] = exp1 = postCompileNewVM(scope, exp->list[0]);
5824  OS_ASSERT(stack_pos+1 == scope->function->stack_cur_size);
5825  if(exp->list[0]->type == EXP_TYPE_SET_UPVALUE || exp->list[0]->type == EXP_TYPE_SET_UPVALUE_NO_POP || exp->list[0]->slots.a < scope->function->num_locals){
5826  Expression * exp_value = exp->list[0];
5827  exp2 = new (malloc(sizeof(Expression) OS_DBG_FILEPOS)) Expression(EXP_TYPE_MOVE, exp->token);
5828  exp2->slots.a = stack_pos;
5829  exp2->slots.b = exp_value->type == EXP_TYPE_MOVE || exp_value->type == EXP_TYPE_SET_UPVALUE || exp_value->type == EXP_TYPE_SET_UPVALUE_NO_POP ? exp_value->slots.b : exp_value->slots.a;
5830  exp2->ret_values = 1;
5831  exp2->list.add(exp_value OS_DBG_FILEPOS);
5832  exp->list[0] = exp2;
5833  }
5834  scope->popTempVar();
5835  exp->list[1] = exp1 = postCompileNewVM(scope, exp->list[1]);
5836  OS_ASSERT(stack_pos == scope->function->stack_cur_size || isError());
5837  if(exp->list.count == 3){
5838  exp->list[2] = exp1 = postCompileNewVM(scope, exp->list[2]);
5839  OS_ASSERT(stack_pos == scope->function->stack_cur_size || isError());
5840  }
5841  return exp;
5842 
5843  case EXP_TYPE_QUESTION:
5844  OS_ASSERT(exp->list.count == 3);
5845  stack_pos = scope->function->stack_cur_size;
5846 
5847  exp->list[0] = exp1 = postCompileNewVM(scope, exp->list[0]);
5848  OS_ASSERT(stack_pos+1 == scope->function->stack_cur_size);
5849  scope->popTempVar();
5850 
5851  exp->list[1] = exp1 = postCompileNewVM(scope, exp->list[1]);
5852  OS_ASSERT(stack_pos+1 == scope->function->stack_cur_size);
5853  scope->popTempVar();
5854 
5855  exp->list[2] = exp1 = postCompileNewVM(scope, exp->list[2]);
5856  OS_ASSERT(stack_pos+1 == scope->function->stack_cur_size);
5857  exp->slots.a = stack_pos; // exp1->slots.a;
5858  return exp;
5859 
5860  case EXP_TYPE_DEBUG_LOCALS:
5861  OS_ASSERT(exp->list.count == 1);
5862  exp1 = postCompileNewVM(scope, exp->list[0]);
5863  allocator->vectorClear(exp->list);
5864  allocator->deleteObj(exp);
5865  return exp1;
5866 
5867  case EXP_TYPE_ARRAY:
5868  case EXP_TYPE_OBJECT:
5869  exp->slots.a = scope->allocTempVar();
5870  break;
5871 
5872  case EXP_TYPE_OBJECT_SET_BY_NAME:
5873  OS_ASSERT(exp->list.count == 1);
5874 
5875  stack_pos = scope->allocTempVar();
5876  b = -1 - exp->slots.b - prog_numbers.count - CONST_STD_VALUES; // const string
5877  if(b < -OS_MAX_GENERIC_CONST_INDEX){
5878  exp_xconst = new (malloc(sizeof(Expression) OS_DBG_FILEPOS)) Expression(EXP_TYPE_GET_XCONST, exp->token);
5879  exp_xconst->slots.b = b;
5880  exp_xconst->slots.a = b = stack_pos;
5881  exp_xconst->ret_values = 1;
5882  }else exp_xconst = NULL;
5883 
5884  exp->type = EXP_TYPE_INIT_PROPERTY;
5885  OS_ASSERT(scope->function->stack_cur_size > scope->function->num_locals);
5886  exp->slots.a = scope->function->stack_cur_size-2;
5887  exp->slots.b = b;
5888  exp->list[0] = exp1 = postCompileNewVM(scope, exp->list[0]);
5889  exp->slots.c = exp1->slots.a;
5890  scope->popTempVar(2);
5891  // TODO: is it really needed to check slot here?
5892  // don't optimize assignment of local var
5893  if(exp1->type == EXP_TYPE_MOVE && exp1->slots.a >= scope->function->num_locals){ // && (exp1->slots.b < 0 || exp1->slots.b >= scope->function->num_locals)){
5894  exp->slots.c = exp1->slots.b;
5895  exp1->type = EXP_TYPE_NOP;
5896  }
5897  return Lib::addXconst(this, exp, exp_xconst);
5898 
5899  case EXP_TYPE_OBJECT_SET_BY_INDEX:
5900  OS_ASSERT(exp->list.count == 1);
5901 
5902  stack_pos = scope->allocTempVar();
5903  b = -1 - exp->slots.b - CONST_STD_VALUES; // const index
5904  if(b < -OS_MAX_GENERIC_CONST_INDEX){
5905  exp_xconst = new (malloc(sizeof(Expression) OS_DBG_FILEPOS)) Expression(EXP_TYPE_GET_XCONST, exp->token);
5906  exp_xconst->slots.b = b;
5907  exp_xconst->slots.a = b = stack_pos;
5908  exp_xconst->ret_values = 1;
5909  }else exp_xconst = NULL;
5910 
5911  exp->type = EXP_TYPE_INIT_PROPERTY;
5912  OS_ASSERT(scope->function->stack_cur_size > scope->function->num_locals);
5913  exp->slots.a = scope->function->stack_cur_size-2;
5914  exp->slots.b = b;
5915  exp->list[0] = exp1 = postCompileNewVM(scope, exp->list[0]);
5916  exp->slots.c = exp1->slots.a;
5917  scope->popTempVar(2);
5918  // TODO: is it really needed to check slot here?
5919  // don't optimize assignment of local var
5920  if(exp1->type == EXP_TYPE_MOVE && exp1->slots.a >= scope->function->num_locals){ // && (exp1->slots.b < 0 || exp1->slots.b >= scope->function->num_locals)){
5921  exp->slots.c = exp1->slots.b;
5922  exp1->type = EXP_TYPE_NOP;
5923  }
5924  return Lib::addXconst(this, exp, exp_xconst);
5925 
5926  case EXP_TYPE_OBJECT_SET_BY_EXP:
5927  OS_ASSERT(exp->list.count == 2);
5928  exp->type = EXP_TYPE_INIT_PROPERTY;
5929  OS_ASSERT(scope->function->stack_cur_size > scope->function->num_locals);
5930  exp->slots.a = scope->function->stack_cur_size-1;
5931  exp->list[0] = exp1 = postCompileNewVM(scope, exp->list[0]);
5932  exp->list[1] = exp2 = postCompileNewVM(scope, exp->list[1]);
5933  exp->slots.b = exp1->slots.a;
5934  exp->slots.c = exp2->slots.a;
5935  scope->popTempVar(2);
5936  // TODO: is it really needed to check slot here?
5937  if(exp1->type == EXP_TYPE_MOVE && exp1->slots.a >= scope->function->num_locals && exp1->slots.b >= 0){ // CONST IS NOT ALLOWED HERE!!!
5938  exp->slots.b = exp1->slots.b;
5939  exp1->type = EXP_TYPE_NOP;
5940  }
5941  // TODO: is it really needed to check slot here?
5942  // don't optimize assignment of local var
5943  if(exp2->type == EXP_TYPE_MOVE && exp2->slots.a >= scope->function->num_locals){ // && (exp2->slots.b < 0 || exp2->slots.b >= scope->function->num_locals)){
5944  exp->slots.c = exp2->slots.b;
5945  exp2->type = EXP_TYPE_NOP;
5946  }
5947  return exp;
5948 
5949  case EXP_TYPE_OBJECT_SET_BY_AUTO_INDEX:
5950  stack_pos = scope->function->stack_cur_size;
5951 
5952  exp->type = EXP_TYPE_CALL_METHOD;
5953  exp->ret_values = 0;
5954 
5955  exp1 = new (malloc(sizeof(Expression) OS_DBG_FILEPOS)) Expression(EXP_TYPE_PARAMS, exp->token);
5956  exp1->list.swap(exp->list);
5957  exp1->ret_values = 1;
5958 
5959  exp2 = new (malloc(sizeof(Expression) OS_DBG_FILEPOS)) Expression(EXP_TYPE_MOVE, exp->token);
5960  exp2->slots.a = scope->allocTempVar();
5961  exp2->slots.b = scope->function->stack_cur_size-2;
5962  exp2->ret_values = 1;
5963  exp->list.add(exp2 OS_DBG_FILEPOS);
5964  exp->list.add(exp1 OS_DBG_FILEPOS);
5965 
5966  exp2 = new (malloc(sizeof(Expression) OS_DBG_FILEPOS)) Expression(EXP_TYPE_MOVE, exp->token);
5967  exp2->slots.a = scope->allocTempVar();
5968  exp2->slots.b = -1 - exp->slots.b - prog_numbers.count - CONST_STD_VALUES; // const string
5969  exp2->ret_values = 1;
5970  allocator->vectorInsertAtIndex(exp1->list, 0, exp2 OS_DBG_FILEPOS);
5971 
5972  if(exp2->slots.b < -OS_MAX_GENERIC_CONST_INDEX){
5973  exp2->type = EXP_TYPE_GET_XCONST;
5974  }
5975 
5976  exp1->list[1] = postCompileNewVM(scope, exp1->list[1]);
5977  OS_ASSERT(scope->function->stack_cur_size - stack_pos == 3);
5978  exp->slots.a = stack_pos;
5979  exp->slots.b = 3;
5980  exp->slots.c = 0;
5981  scope->function->stack_cur_size = stack_pos;
5982  return exp;
5983 
5984  case EXP_TYPE_OBJECT_CREATE_CONST:
5985  OS_ASSERT(exp->list.count == 1 && exp->list[0]->ret_values == 1 && exp->ret_values == 0);
5986  stack_pos = scope->function->stack_cur_size;
5987 
5988  scope->allocTempVar();
5989  scope->allocTempVar();
5990  scope->allocTempVar();
5991  scope->allocTempVar();
5992 
5993  exp1 = new (malloc(sizeof(Expression) OS_DBG_FILEPOS)) Expression(EXP_TYPE_PARAMS, exp->token);
5994  exp1->list.swap(exp->list);
5995  exp1->ret_values = 4;
5996 
5997  exp2 = new (malloc(sizeof(Expression) OS_DBG_FILEPOS)) Expression(EXP_TYPE_MOVE, exp->token);
5998  exp2->slots.a = stack_pos + 0;
5999  exp2->slots.b = scope->function->num_params + POST_VAR_GLOBALS;
6000  exp2->ret_values = 1;
6001  exp->list.add(exp2 OS_DBG_FILEPOS);
6002  exp->list.add(exp1 OS_DBG_FILEPOS);
6003 
6004  exp2 = new (malloc(sizeof(Expression) OS_DBG_FILEPOS)) Expression(EXP_TYPE_MOVE, exp->token);
6005  exp2->slots.a = stack_pos + 3;
6006  exp2->slots.b = -1 - exp->slots.b - prog_numbers.count - CONST_STD_VALUES; // prop name
6007  exp2->ret_values = 1;
6008  allocator->vectorInsertAtIndex(exp1->list, 0, exp2 OS_DBG_FILEPOS);
6009 
6010  if(exp2->slots.b < -OS_MAX_GENERIC_CONST_INDEX){
6011  exp2->type = EXP_TYPE_GET_XCONST;
6012  }
6013 
6014  exp2 = new (malloc(sizeof(Expression) OS_DBG_FILEPOS)) Expression(EXP_TYPE_MOVE, exp->token);
6015  exp2->slots.a = stack_pos + 2;
6016  exp2->slots.b = stack_pos - 1; // this to the first param
6017  exp2->ret_values = 1;
6018  allocator->vectorInsertAtIndex(exp1->list, 0, exp2 OS_DBG_FILEPOS);
6019 
6020  exp2 = new (malloc(sizeof(Expression) OS_DBG_FILEPOS)) Expression(EXP_TYPE_MOVE, exp->token);
6021  exp2->slots.a = stack_pos + 1;
6022  exp2->slots.b = -1 - exp->slots.c - prog_numbers.count - CONST_STD_VALUES; // func name
6023  exp2->ret_values = 1;
6024  allocator->vectorInsertAtIndex(exp1->list, 0, exp2 OS_DBG_FILEPOS);
6025 
6026  if(exp2->slots.b < -OS_MAX_GENERIC_CONST_INDEX){
6027  exp2->type = EXP_TYPE_GET_XCONST;
6028  }
6029 
6030  OS_ASSERT(exp1->list.count == 4);
6031  exp1 = postCompileNewVM(scope, exp1);
6032 
6033  exp->type = EXP_TYPE_CALL_METHOD;
6034  exp->ret_values = 0;
6035  OS_ASSERT(scope->function->stack_cur_size - stack_pos == 5);
6036  exp->slots.a = stack_pos;
6037  exp->slots.b = 5;
6038  exp->slots.c = 0;
6039 
6040  scope->function->stack_cur_size = stack_pos;
6041  return exp;
6042 
6043  case EXP_TYPE_CONST_NUMBER:
6044  OS_ASSERT(exp->list.count == 0);
6045  exp->slots.a = scope->allocTempVar();
6046  exp->slots.b = -1 - exp->slots.b - CONST_STD_VALUES;
6047  exp->type = exp->slots.b < -OS_MAX_GENERIC_CONST_INDEX ? EXP_TYPE_GET_XCONST : EXP_TYPE_MOVE;
6048  OS_ASSERT(exp->ret_values == 1);
6049  return exp;
6050 
6051  case EXP_TYPE_CONST_STRING:
6052  OS_ASSERT(exp->list.count == 0);
6053  exp->slots.a = scope->allocTempVar();
6054  exp->slots.b = -1 - exp->slots.b - prog_numbers.count - CONST_STD_VALUES;
6055  exp->type = exp->slots.b < -OS_MAX_GENERIC_CONST_INDEX ? EXP_TYPE_GET_XCONST : EXP_TYPE_MOVE;
6056  OS_ASSERT(exp->ret_values == 1);
6057  return exp;
6058 
6059  case EXP_TYPE_CONST_NULL:
6060  OS_ASSERT(exp->list.count == 0);
6061  exp->slots.a = scope->allocTempVar();
6062  exp->slots.b = -1 - CONST_NULL;
6063  exp->type = exp->slots.b < -OS_MAX_GENERIC_CONST_INDEX ? EXP_TYPE_GET_XCONST : EXP_TYPE_MOVE;
6064  return exp;
6065 
6066  case EXP_TYPE_CONST_FALSE:
6067  OS_ASSERT(exp->list.count == 0);
6068  exp->slots.a = scope->allocTempVar();
6069  exp->slots.b = -1 - CONST_FALSE;
6070  exp->type = exp->slots.b < -OS_MAX_GENERIC_CONST_INDEX ? EXP_TYPE_GET_XCONST : EXP_TYPE_MOVE;
6071  return exp;
6072 
6073  case EXP_TYPE_CONST_TRUE:
6074  OS_ASSERT(exp->list.count == 0);
6075  exp->slots.a = scope->allocTempVar();
6076  exp->slots.b = -1 - CONST_TRUE;
6077  exp->type = exp->slots.b < -OS_MAX_GENERIC_CONST_INDEX ? EXP_TYPE_GET_XCONST : EXP_TYPE_MOVE;
6078  return exp;
6079 
6080  case EXP_TYPE_GET_THIS:
6081  OS_ASSERT(exp->list.count == 0);
6082  exp->slots.a = scope->allocTempVar();
6083  exp->slots.b = PRE_VAR_THIS;
6084  exp->type = EXP_TYPE_MOVE;
6085  return exp;
6086 
6087  case EXP_TYPE_SUPER:
6088  case EXP_TYPE_GET_ARGUMENTS:
6089  case EXP_TYPE_GET_REST_ARGUMENTS:
6090  OS_ASSERT(exp->list.count == 0);
6091  exp->slots.a = scope->allocTempVar();
6092  return exp;
6093 
6094  case EXP_TYPE_LOGIC_NOT: // !
6095  OS_ASSERT(exp->list.count == 1);
6096  stack_pos = scope->function->stack_cur_size;
6097  exp1 = postCompileNewVM(scope, exp->list[0]);
6098  OS_ASSERT(stack_pos+1 == scope->function->stack_cur_size);
6099  if(exp1->type == EXP_TYPE_LOGIC_NOT){
6100  OS_ASSERT(exp1->list.count == 1);
6101  exp->type = EXP_TYPE_LOGIC_BOOL;
6102  exp->list[0] = exp1->list[0];
6103  exp->slots = exp1->slots;
6104  allocator->vectorRemoveAtIndex(exp1->list, 0);
6105  allocator->deleteObj(exp1);
6106  return exp;
6107  }
6108  if(exp1->type == EXP_TYPE_LOGIC_BOOL){
6109  OS_ASSERT(exp1->list.count == 1);
6110  exp->list[0] = exp1->list[0];
6111  exp->slots = exp1->slots;
6112  allocator->vectorRemoveAtIndex(exp1->list, 0);
6113  allocator->deleteObj(exp1);
6114  return exp;
6115  }
6116  exp->list[0] = exp1;
6117  OS_ASSERT(exp1->ret_values == 1);
6118  exp->slots.a = stack_pos;
6119  exp->slots.b = stack_pos;
6120  return exp;
6121 
6122  case EXP_TYPE_LOGIC_BOOL: // !
6123  OS_ASSERT(exp->list.count == 1);
6124  stack_pos = scope->function->stack_cur_size;
6125  exp1 = postCompileNewVM(scope, exp->list[0]);
6126  OS_ASSERT(stack_pos+1 == scope->function->stack_cur_size);
6127  if(exp1->type == EXP_TYPE_LOGIC_NOT || exp1->type == EXP_TYPE_LOGIC_BOOL){
6128  allocator->vectorRemoveAtIndex(exp->list, 0);
6129  allocator->deleteObj(exp);
6130  return exp1;
6131  }
6132  exp->list[0] = exp1;
6133  OS_ASSERT(exp1->ret_values == 1);
6134  exp->slots.a = stack_pos;
6135  exp->slots.b = stack_pos;
6136  return exp;
6137 
6138  case EXP_TYPE_CONCAT:
6139  case EXP_TYPE_BEFORE_INJECT_VAR:
6140  case EXP_TYPE_AFTER_INJECT_VAR:
6141  OS_ASSERT(exp->list.count == 2 && exp->ret_values == 1);
