6601  exp->list.insert(0, exp2 OS_DBG_FILEPOS);
6602 
6603  exp2 = new (malloc(sizeof(Expression) OS_DBG_FILEPOS)) Expression(exp_type, exp->token);
6604  exp2->slots.a = stack_pos; // scope->function->stack_cur_size-1;
6605  exp2->slots.b = exp2->slots.a;
6606  exp2->slots.c = exp1->slots.b;
6607  exp2->ret_values = 1;
6608  exp->list.insert(1, exp2 OS_DBG_FILEPOS);
6609 
6610  for(i = 0; i < exp1->list.count; i++){
6611  exp->list.insert(i, exp1->list[i] OS_DBG_FILEPOS);
6612  }
6613  allocator->vectorClear(exp1->list);
6614 
6615  exp->slots.a = exp1->slots.b = exp2->slots.a;
6616  break;
6617 
6618  case EXP_TYPE_SET_PROPERTY:
6619  case EXP_TYPE_SET_PROPERTY_NO_POP:
6620  exp2 = new (malloc(sizeof(Expression) OS_DBG_FILEPOS)) Expression(EXP_TYPE_GET_PROPERTY, exp1->token);
6621  exp2->slots.a = stack_pos; // scope->allocTempVar();
6622  exp2->slots.b = exp1->slots.a;
6623  exp2->slots.c = exp1->slots.b;
6624  exp2->ret_values = 1;
6625  exp->list.insert(0, exp2 OS_DBG_FILEPOS);
6626 
6627  exp2 = new (malloc(sizeof(Expression) OS_DBG_FILEPOS)) Expression(exp_type, exp->token);
6628  exp2->slots.a = stack_pos; // scope->function->stack_cur_size-1;
6629  exp2->slots.b = exp2->slots.a;
6630  exp2->slots.c = exp1->slots.c;
6631  exp2->ret_values = 1;
6632  exp->list.insert(1, exp2 OS_DBG_FILEPOS);
6633 
6634  for(i = 0; i < exp1->list.count; i++){
6635  exp->list.insert(i, exp1->list[i] OS_DBG_FILEPOS);
6636  }
6637  allocator->vectorClear(exp1->list);
6638 
6639  exp->slots.a = exp1->slots.c = exp2->slots.a;
6640  break;
6641 
6642  default:
6643  // EXP_TYPE_GET_PROPERTY is not implemented yet
6644  setError(ERROR_SYNTAX, exp1->token);
6645  // allocator->deleteObj(exp);
6646  return exp;
6647  }
6648  scope->function->stack_cur_size = stack_pos + exp->ret_values;
6649  OS_ASSERT(scope->function->stack_cur_size >= scope->function->num_locals && scope->function->stack_cur_size <= scope->function->stack_size);
6650 
6651  // exp->slots.b = 0;
6652  exp->type = EXP_TYPE_CODE_LIST;
6653 
6654  return exp;
6655 
6656  // case EXP_TYPE_CONCAT:
6657  case EXP_TYPE_BIT_AND:
6658  case EXP_TYPE_BIT_OR:
6659  case EXP_TYPE_BIT_XOR:
6660  case EXP_TYPE_COMPARE:
6661  case EXP_TYPE_ADD: // +
6662  case EXP_TYPE_SUB: // -
6663  case EXP_TYPE_MUL: // *
6664  case EXP_TYPE_DIV: // /
6665  case EXP_TYPE_MOD: // %
6666  case EXP_TYPE_LSHIFT: // <<
6667  case EXP_TYPE_RSHIFT: // >>
6668  case EXP_TYPE_POW: // **
6669  OS_ASSERT(exp->list.count == 2);
6670  stack_pos = scope->function->stack_cur_size;
6671  exp = Lib::processList(this, scope, exp);
6672  exp1 = exp->list[0];
6673  exp2 = exp->list[1];
6674  OS_ASSERT(stack_pos+2 == scope->function->stack_cur_size);
6675  exp->slots.a = stack_pos;
6676  exp->slots.b = stack_pos;
6677  exp->slots.c = stack_pos+1;
6678  scope->popTempVar();
6679  // TODO: is it really needed to check slot here?
6680  // don't optimize assignment of local var
6681  if(exp1->type == EXP_TYPE_MOVE && exp1->slots.a >= scope->function->num_locals){ // && (exp1->slots.b < 0 || exp1->slots.b >= scope->function->num_locals)){
6682  exp->slots.b = exp1->slots.b;
6683  exp1->type = EXP_TYPE_NOP;
6684  }
6685  // TODO: is it really needed to check slot here?
6686  // don't optimize assignment of local var
6687  if(exp2->type == EXP_TYPE_MOVE && exp1->slots.a >= scope->function->num_locals){ // && (exp2->slots.b < 0 || exp2->slots.b >= scope->function->num_locals)){
6688  exp->slots.c = exp2->slots.b;
6689  exp2->type = EXP_TYPE_NOP;
6690  }
6691  return exp;
6692 
6693  case EXP_TYPE_LOGIC_PTR_EQ:
6694  case EXP_TYPE_LOGIC_PTR_NE:
6695  case EXP_TYPE_LOGIC_EQ:
6696  case EXP_TYPE_LOGIC_NE:
6697  case EXP_TYPE_LOGIC_GE:
6698  case EXP_TYPE_LOGIC_LE:
6699  case EXP_TYPE_LOGIC_GREATER:
6700  case EXP_TYPE_LOGIC_LESS:
6701  OS_ASSERT(exp->list.count == 2);
6702  stack_pos = scope->function->stack_cur_size;
6703  exp = Lib::processList(this, scope, exp);
6704  OS_ASSERT(stack_pos+2 == scope->function->stack_cur_size);
6705  exp->slots.a = stack_pos;
6706  exp->slots.b = 0;
6707  exp->slots.c = 0;
6708  scope->popTempVar();
6709  return exp;
6710 
6711  case EXP_TYPE_GET_LOCAL_VAR:
6712  case EXP_TYPE_GET_LOCAL_VAR_AUTO_CREATE:
6713  exp = Lib::processList(this, scope, exp);
6714  if(exp->local_var.up_count){
6715  exp->type = EXP_TYPE_GET_UPVALUE;
6716  exp->slots.a = scope->allocTempVar();
6717  exp->slots.b = exp->local_var.index;
6718  exp->slots.c = exp->local_var.up_count;
6719  registerUpvalue(scope, exp);
6720  }else{
6721  exp->type = EXP_TYPE_MOVE;
6722  exp->slots.a = scope->allocTempVar();
6723  exp->slots.b = exp->local_var.index;
6724  }
6725  return exp;
6726 
6727  case EXP_TYPE_SET_LOCAL_VAR:
6728  case EXP_TYPE_SET_LOCAL_VAR_NO_POP:
6729  OS_ASSERT(exp->list.count == 1);
6730  no_pop = exp->type == EXP_TYPE_SET_LOCAL_VAR_NO_POP;
6731  stack_pos = scope->function->stack_cur_size;
6732  exp = Lib::processList(this, scope, exp);
6733  OS_ASSERT(stack_pos < scope->function->stack_cur_size);
6734  if(exp->local_var.up_count){
6735  exp->type = EXP_TYPE_SET_UPVALUE;
6736  exp->slots.a = exp->local_var.index;
6737  exp->slots.b = --scope->function->stack_cur_size;
6738  exp->slots.c = exp->local_var.up_count;
6739  registerUpvalue(scope, exp);
6740  }else{
6741  exp->type = EXP_TYPE_MOVE;
6742  exp->slots.a = exp->local_var.index;
6743  exp->slots.b = --scope->function->stack_cur_size;
6744  }
6745  if(no_pop){
6746  scope->function->stack_cur_size++;
6747  OS_ASSERT(scope->function->stack_cur_size >= scope->function->num_locals && scope->function->stack_cur_size <= scope->function->stack_size);
6748  return exp;
6749  }
6750  exp1 = exp->list[0];
6751  if(exp1->type == EXP_TYPE_PARAMS || exp1->type == EXP_TYPE_CODE_LIST){
6752  OS_ASSERT(exp1->list.count > 0);
6753  exp1 = exp1->list.lastElement();
6754  }
6755  // TODO: is it really needed to check slot here?
6756  // don't optimize assignment of local var
6757  // if(exp1->type == EXP_TYPE_MOVE && (exp1->slots.b < 0 || exp1->slots.b >= scope->function->num_locals)){
6758  /* if(exp1->type == EXP_TYPE_MOVE){ // CONST IS ALLOWED HERE!!! && exp1->slots.b >= scope->function->num_locals){ // stack_cur_size is already decremented
6759  exp->slots.b = exp1->slots.b;
6760  exp1->type = EXP_TYPE_NOP;
6761  // return exp;
6762  } */
6763  if(exp->type == EXP_TYPE_MOVE
6764  && Lib::allowOverrideOpcodeResult(exp1)
6765  && exp1->slots.a >= scope->function->num_locals
6766  )
6767  {
6768  exp1->slots.a = exp->slots.a;
6769  exp->type = EXP_TYPE_NOP;
6770  }
6771  return exp;
6772 
6773  case EXP_TYPE_SET_PROPERTY:
6774  case EXP_TYPE_SET_PROPERTY_NO_POP:
6775  case EXP_TYPE_INIT_PROPERTY:
6776  OS_ASSERT(exp->list.count == 3);
6777  no_pop = exp->type == EXP_TYPE_SET_PROPERTY_NO_POP;
6778  stack_pos = scope->function->stack_cur_size;
6779  exp = Lib::processList(this, scope, exp);
6780  OS_ASSERT(stack_pos+3 <= scope->function->stack_cur_size);
6781  stack_pos = scope->function->stack_cur_size - 3;
6782  exp->slots.a = stack_pos + 1;
6783  exp->slots.b = stack_pos + 2;
6784  exp->slots.c = stack_pos;
6785  scope->function->stack_cur_size = stack_pos;
6786  exp1 = exp->list[0];
6787  // TODO: is it really needed to check slot here?
6788  // don't optimize assignment of local var
6789  if(exp1->type == EXP_TYPE_MOVE && exp1->slots.a >= scope->function->num_locals){ // && (exp1->slots.b < 0 || exp1->slots.b >= scope->function->num_locals)){
6790  exp->slots.c = exp1->slots.b;
6791  exp1->type = EXP_TYPE_NOP;
6792  }
6793  exp1 = exp->list[1];
6794  // TODO: is it really needed to check slot here?
6795  // don't optimize assignment of local var
6796  if(exp1->type == EXP_TYPE_MOVE && exp1->slots.a >= scope->function->num_locals){ // && (exp1->slots.b < 0 || exp1->slots.b >= scope->function->num_locals)){
6797  exp->slots.a = exp1->slots.b;
6798  exp1->type = EXP_TYPE_NOP;
6799  }
6800  exp1 = exp->list[2];
6801  // TODO: is it really needed to check slot here?
6802  // don't optimize assignment of local var
6803  if(exp1->type == EXP_TYPE_MOVE && exp1->slots.a >= scope->function->num_locals){ // && (exp1->slots.b < 0 || exp1->slots.b >= scope->function->num_locals)){
6804  exp->slots.b = exp1->slots.b;
6805  exp1->type = EXP_TYPE_NOP;
6806  }
6807  if(no_pop){
6808  Expression * exp_value = new (malloc(sizeof(Expression) OS_DBG_FILEPOS)) Expression(EXP_TYPE_MOVE, exp->token, exp OS_DBG_FILEPOS);
6809  exp_value->slots.a = scope->allocTempVar();
6810  exp_value->slots.b = exp->slots.c;
6811  exp_value->ret_values = 1;
6812  if(exp_value->slots.b < -OS_MAX_GENERIC_CONST_INDEX){
6813  exp_value->type = EXP_TYPE_GET_XCONST;
6814  }
6815  return exp_value;
6816  }
6817  return exp;
6818 
6819  case EXP_TYPE_GET_ENV_VAR:
6820  case EXP_TYPE_GET_ENV_VAR_AUTO_CREATE:
6821  OS_ASSERT(exp->list.count == 0);
6822  exp->slots.a = scope->allocTempVar();
6823  exp->slots.c = -1 - exp->slots.b - prog_numbers.count - CONST_STD_VALUES;
6824  exp->slots.b = scope->function->num_params + POST_VAR_ENV;
6825  exp->type = EXP_TYPE_GET_PROPERTY;
6826 
6827  if(exp->slots.c < -OS_MAX_GENERIC_CONST_INDEX){
6828  exp_xconst = new (malloc(sizeof(Expression) OS_DBG_FILEPOS)) Expression(EXP_TYPE_GET_XCONST, exp->token);
6829  exp_xconst->slots.b = exp->slots.c;
6830  exp_xconst->slots.a = exp->slots.c = exp->slots.a;
6831  exp_xconst->ret_values = 1;
6832  return Lib::addXconst(this, exp, exp_xconst);
6833  }
6834  return exp;
6835 
6836  case EXP_TYPE_SET_ENV_VAR:
6837  case EXP_TYPE_SET_ENV_VAR_NO_POP:
6838  OS_ASSERT(exp->list.count == 1);
6839  no_pop = exp->type == EXP_TYPE_SET_ENV_VAR_NO_POP;
6840  stack_pos = scope->function->stack_cur_size;
6841  exp = Lib::processList(this, scope, exp);
6842  OS_ASSERT(stack_pos < scope->function->stack_cur_size);
6843  exp->slots.a = scope->function->num_params + POST_VAR_ENV;
6844  exp->slots.b = -1 - exp->slots.b - prog_numbers.count - CONST_STD_VALUES;
6845  exp->slots.c = --scope->function->stack_cur_size;
6846  exp->type = EXP_TYPE_SET_PROPERTY;
6847 
6848  if(exp->slots.b < -OS_MAX_GENERIC_CONST_INDEX){
6849  exp_xconst = new (malloc(sizeof(Expression) OS_DBG_FILEPOS)) Expression(EXP_TYPE_GET_XCONST, exp->token);
6850  exp_xconst->slots.b = exp->slots.b;
6851  exp_xconst->slots.a = exp->slots.b = exp->slots.c + 1;
6852  exp_xconst->ret_values = 1;
6853  if(exp_xconst->slots.a >= scope->function->stack_size){
6854  scope->function->stack_size = exp_xconst->slots.a + 1;
6855  }
6856  exp->list.add(exp_xconst OS_DBG_FILEPOS);
6857  }
6858  // exp1 = exp->list[0];
6859  if(no_pop){
6860  scope->function->stack_cur_size++;
6861  OS_ASSERT(scope->function->stack_cur_size >= scope->function->num_locals && scope->function->stack_cur_size <= scope->function->stack_size);
6862  return exp;
6863  }
6864  return exp;
6865 
6866  case EXP_TYPE_GET_PROPERTY_AUTO_CREATE:
6867  exp->type = EXP_TYPE_GET_PROPERTY;
6868  // no break
6869 
6870  case EXP_TYPE_GET_PROPERTY:
6871  OS_ASSERT(exp->list.count == 2);
6872  stack_pos = scope->function->stack_cur_size;
6873  exp = Lib::processList(this, scope, exp);
6874  OS_ASSERT(stack_pos+2 == scope->function->stack_cur_size);
6875  exp1 = exp->list[0];
6876  exp2 = exp->list[1];
6877  exp->slots.a = stack_pos;
6878  exp->slots.b = stack_pos; // exp1->slots.a;
6879  exp->slots.c = stack_pos + 1; // exp2->slots.a;
6880  scope->popTempVar();
6881  // TODO: is it really needed to check slot here?
6882  if(exp1->type == EXP_TYPE_MOVE && exp1->slots.a >= scope->function->num_locals && exp1->slots.b >= 0){ // CONST IS NOT ALLOWED HERE!!!
6883  exp->slots.b = exp1->slots.b;
6884  exp1->type = EXP_TYPE_NOP;
6885  }
6886  // TODO: is it really needed to check slot here?
6887  // don't optimize assignment of local var
6888  if(exp2->type == EXP_TYPE_MOVE && exp2->slots.a >= scope->function->num_locals){ // && (exp2->slots.b < 0 || exp2->slots.b >= scope->function->num_locals)){
6889  exp->slots.c = exp2->slots.b;
6890  exp2->type = EXP_TYPE_NOP;
6891  }
6892  return exp;
6893 
6894  case EXP_TYPE_CASE:
6895  case EXP_TYPE_CASE_DEFAULT:
6896  case EXP_TYPE_CASE_JUMP:
6897  return exp;
6898  }
6899  return Lib::processList(this, scope, exp);
6900 }
6901 
6902 OS::Core::Compiler::Scope * OS::Core::Compiler::expectTextExpression()
6903 {
6904  OS_ASSERT(recent_token);
6905 
6906  Scope * scope = new (malloc(sizeof(Scope) OS_DBG_FILEPOS)) Scope(NULL, EXP_TYPE_FUNCTION, recent_token);
6907  scope->parser_started = true;
6908  scope->ret_values = 1;
6909  scope->addPreVars();
6910  scope->num_params = scope->num_locals;
6911  scope->addPostVars();
6912 
6913  Params p = Params()
6914  .setAllowAssign(true)
6915  .setAllowAutoCall(true)
6916  .setAllowBinaryOperator(true)
6917  .setAllowParams(true)
6918  .setAllowRootBlocks(true);
6919 
6920  Expression * exp;
6921  ExpressionList list(allocator);
6922 
6923  while(!isError()){
6924  exp = expectSingleExpression(scope, p);
6925  if(isError()){
6926  break;
6927  }
6928  if(exp){
6929  list.add(exp OS_DBG_FILEPOS);
6930  }
6931  if(!recent_token){
6932  break;
6933  }
6934  TokenType token_type = recent_token->type;
6935  if(token_type == Tokenizer::CODE_SEPARATOR){
6936  if(!readToken()){
6937  break;
6938  }
6939  token_type = recent_token->type;
6940  }
6941  if(token_type == Tokenizer::END_ARRAY_BLOCK
6942  || token_type == Tokenizer::END_BRACKET_BLOCK
6943  || token_type == Tokenizer::END_CODE_BLOCK)
6944  {
6945  break;
6946  }
6947  }
6948  if(isError()){
6949  allocator->deleteObj(scope);
6950  return NULL;
6951  }
6952  if(recent_token){
6953  setError(ERROR_SYNTAX, recent_token);
6954  allocator->deleteObj(scope);
6955  return NULL;
6956  }
6957  if(list.count == 0){
6958  return scope;
6959  }
6960 
6961  bool ret_eval_value = false;
6962  int ret_values = list.count == 1 && list[0]->ret_values > 0 && list[0]->type == EXP_TYPE_FUNCTION ? 1 : 0;
6963  if(!ret_values){
6964  bool is_eval = tokenizer->getTextData()->filename.isEmpty();
6965  if(is_eval){
6966  exp = newExpressionFromList(list, 1, true);
6967  ret_eval_value = true;
6968  }else{
6969  putNextTokenType(Tokenizer::CODE_SEPARATOR);
6970  readToken();
6971 
6972  TokenData * name_token = new (malloc(sizeof(TokenData) OS_DBG_FILEPOS)) TokenData(tokenizer->getTextData(),
6973  allocator->core->strings->var_env,
6974  Tokenizer::NAME, recent_token->line, recent_token->pos);
6975 
6976  ExpressionList& func_exp_list = ret_values == 1 ? list[0]->list : list;
6977  Expression * name_exp = new (malloc(sizeof(Expression) OS_DBG_FILEPOS)) Expression(EXP_TYPE_GET_LOCAL_VAR, name_token);
6978  name_exp->ret_values = 1;
6979  if(!findLocalVar(name_exp->local_var, scope, allocator->core->strings->var_env, scope->num_locals, false)){
6980  OS_ASSERT(false);
6981  }
6982  OS_ASSERT(name_exp->local_var.up_count == 0);
6983  Expression * ret_exp = new (malloc(sizeof(Expression) OS_DBG_FILEPOS)) Expression(EXP_TYPE_RETURN, recent_token, name_exp OS_DBG_FILEPOS);
6984  ret_exp->ret_values = 1;
6985  func_exp_list.add(ret_exp OS_DBG_FILEPOS);
6986 
6987  name_token->release();
6988 
6989  exp = newExpressionFromList(list, ret_values);
6990  }
6991  }else{
6992  exp = newExpressionFromList(list, ret_values);
6993  }
6994  switch(exp->type){
6995  case EXP_TYPE_CODE_LIST:
6996  if(!ret_eval_value && exp->list.count == 1 && exp->list[0]->type == EXP_TYPE_FUNCTION){
6997  allocator->deleteObj(scope);
6998  scope = dynamic_cast<Scope*>(exp->list[0]);
6999  allocator->vectorClear(exp->list);
7000  allocator->deleteObj(exp);
7001  return scope;
7002  }
7003  // exp = expectExpressionValues(exp, 0);
7004  scope->list.swap(exp->list);
7005  allocator->deleteObj(exp);
7006  break;
7007 
7008  case EXP_TYPE_FUNCTION:
7009  if(!ret_eval_value){
7010  // OS_ASSERT(scope->num_locals == 0);
7011  allocator->deleteObj(scope);
7012  scope = dynamic_cast<Scope*>(exp);
7013  OS_ASSERT(scope);
7014  scope->parent = NULL;
7015  return scope;
7016  }
7017  // no break
7018 
7019  default:
7020  scope->list.add(exp OS_DBG_FILEPOS);
7021  }
7022  if(ret_eval_value && scope->list.count > 0){
7023  Expression * last_exp = scope->list.lastElement();
7024  if(last_exp->ret_values == 1 && last_exp->type != EXP_TYPE_RETURN){
7025  scope->list.lastElement() = new (malloc(sizeof(Expression) OS_DBG_FILEPOS)) Expression(EXP_TYPE_RETURN, last_exp->token, last_exp OS_DBG_FILEPOS);
7026  scope->list.lastElement()->ret_values = 1;
7027  }
7028  }
7029  return scope;
7030 }
7031 
7032 OS::Core::Compiler::Scope * OS::Core::Compiler::expectCodeExpression(Scope * parent)
7033 {
7034  OS_ASSERT(recent_token && recent_token->type == Tokenizer::BEGIN_CODE_BLOCK);
7035  if(!expectToken()){
7036  allocator->deleteObj(parent);
7037  return NULL;
7038  }
7039 
7040  Scope * scope;
7041  bool is_new_func;
7042  if(parent->type == EXP_TYPE_FUNCTION && !parent->parser_started){
7043  scope = parent;
7044  is_new_func = true;
7045  parent->parser_started = true;
7046  }else{
7047  scope = new (malloc(sizeof(Scope) OS_DBG_FILEPOS)) Scope(parent, EXP_TYPE_SCOPE, recent_token);
7048  is_new_func = false;
7049  }
7050 
7051  Params p = Params()
7052  .setAllowAssign(true)
7053  .setAllowAutoCall(true)
7054  .setAllowBinaryOperator(true)
7055  .setAllowParams(true)
7056  .setAllowRootBlocks(true);
7057 
7058  Expression * exp;
7059  ExpressionList list(allocator);
7060  bool last_exp_exists = true;
7061  while(!isError()){
7062  exp = expectSingleExpression(scope, p);
7063  if(isError()){
7064  break;
7065  }
7066  if(exp){
7067  last_exp_exists = true;
7068  list.add(exp OS_DBG_FILEPOS);
7069  }else{
7070  last_exp_exists = false;
7071  }
7072  if(!recent_token){
7073  break;
7074  }
7075  TokenType token_type = recent_token->type;
7076  if(token_type == Tokenizer::CODE_SEPARATOR){
7077  if(!readToken()){
7078  break;
7079  }
7080  token_type = recent_token->type;
7081  }
7082  if(token_type == Tokenizer::END_ARRAY_BLOCK
7083  || token_type == Tokenizer::END_BRACKET_BLOCK
7084  || token_type == Tokenizer::END_CODE_BLOCK)
7085  {
7086  break;
7087  }
7088  }
7089  if(isError()){
7090  allocator->deleteObj(scope);
7091  return NULL;
7092  }
7093  if(!recent_token || recent_token->type != Tokenizer::END_CODE_BLOCK){
7094  setError(Tokenizer::END_CODE_BLOCK, recent_token);
7095  allocator->deleteObj(scope);
7096  return NULL;
7097  }
7098  if(is_new_func && !last_exp_exists && list.count > 0){
7099  list.add(new (malloc(sizeof(Expression) OS_DBG_FILEPOS)) Expression(EXP_TYPE_NOP, recent_token) OS_DBG_FILEPOS);
7100  }
7101  readToken();
7102 
7103  if(list.count == 0){
7104  return scope;
7105  }
7106  if(is_new_func){
7107  exp = newExpressionFromList(list, 1, true);
7108  }else{
7109  exp = newExpressionFromList(list, 0);
7110  }
7111  switch(exp->type){
7112  case EXP_TYPE_CODE_LIST:
7113  {
7114  scope->list.swap(exp->list);
7115  allocator->deleteObj(exp);
7116  break;
7117  }
7118  // no break
7119 
7120  default:
7121  scope->list.add(exp OS_DBG_FILEPOS);
7122  }
7123  if(is_new_func && scope->list.count > 0){
7124  Expression * last_exp = scope->list.lastElement();
7125  if(last_exp->ret_values == 1 && last_exp->type != EXP_TYPE_RETURN){
7126  scope->list.lastElement() = new (malloc(sizeof(Expression) OS_DBG_FILEPOS)) Expression(EXP_TYPE_RETURN, last_exp->token, last_exp OS_DBG_FILEPOS);
7127  scope->list.lastElement()->ret_values = 1;
7128  }
7129  }
7130  return scope;
7131 }
7132 
7133 OS::Core::Compiler::Expression * OS::Core::Compiler::expectObjectOrFunctionExpression(Scope * scope, const Params& org_p, bool allow_finish_exp)
7134 {
7135  OS_ASSERT(recent_token && recent_token->type == Tokenizer::BEGIN_CODE_BLOCK);
7136  if(!expectToken()){
7137  return NULL;
7138  }
7139  if(recent_token->type == Tokenizer::OPERATOR_BIT_OR || recent_token->type == Tokenizer::OPERATOR_LOGIC_OR){ // {|| - no params
7140  Expression * exp = expectFunctionSugarExpression(scope); // {|x, x2| x*x2}
7141  if(!exp){
7142  return NULL;
7143  }
7144  // TODO: process org_p, allow_finish_exp ?
7145  return allow_finish_exp ? finishValueExpression(scope, exp, org_p) : exp;
7146  // return exp;
7147  }
7148  ungetToken();
7149  struct Lib {
7150  Compiler * compiler;
7151  Expression * obj_exp;
7152 
7153  Expression * finishValue(Scope * scope, const Params& p, bool allow_finish_exp)
7154  {
7155  if(!allow_finish_exp){
7156  return obj_exp;
7157  }
7158  return compiler->finishValueExpression(scope, obj_exp, Params(p).setAllowAssign(false).setAllowAutoCall(false));
7159  }
7160 
7161  void * malloc(int size OS_DBG_FILEPOS_DECL)
7162  {
7163  return compiler->malloc(size OS_DBG_FILEPOS_PARAM);
7164  }
7165 
7166  Lib(Compiler * p_compiler, int active_locals)
7167  {
7168  compiler = p_compiler;
7169  obj_exp = new (malloc(sizeof(Expression) OS_DBG_FILEPOS)) Expression(EXP_TYPE_OBJECT, compiler->recent_token);
7170  obj_exp->ret_values = 1;
7171  }
7172 
7173  Expression * error()
7174  {
7175  compiler->allocator->deleteObj(obj_exp);
7176  return NULL;
7177  }
7178 
7179  Expression * error(ErrorType err, TokenData * token)
7180  {
7181  compiler->setError(err, token);
7182  return error();
7183  }
7184 
7185  Expression * error(TokenType err, TokenData * token)
7186  {
7187  compiler->setError(err, token);
7188  return error();
7189  }
7190 
7191  } lib(this, scope->function->num_locals);
7192 
7193  Params p = Params().setAllowBinaryOperator(true);
7194 
7195  for(readToken();;){
7196  Expression * exp = NULL;
7197  if(!recent_token){
7198  return lib.error(ERROR_SYNTAX, recent_token);
7199  }
7200  if(recent_token->type == Tokenizer::END_CODE_BLOCK){
7201  readToken();
7202  return lib.finishValue(scope, org_p, allow_finish_exp);
7203  }
7204  TokenData * name_token = recent_token;
7205  if(name_token->type == Tokenizer::BEGIN_ARRAY_BLOCK){
7206  readToken();
7207  TokenData * save_token = recent_token;
7208  exp = expectSingleExpression(scope, p);
7209  if(!exp){
7210  return lib.error();
7211  }
7212  if(exp->ret_values < 1){
7213  allocator->deleteObj(exp);
7214  return lib.error(ERROR_EXPECT_VALUE, save_token);
7215  }
7216  exp = expectExpressionValues(exp, 1);
7217  if(!recent_token || recent_token->type != Tokenizer::END_ARRAY_BLOCK){
7218  allocator->deleteObj(exp);
7219  return lib.error(Tokenizer::END_ARRAY_BLOCK, recent_token);
7220  }
7221  if(!readToken() || (recent_token->type != Tokenizer::OPERATOR_COLON && recent_token->type != Tokenizer::OPERATOR_ASSIGN)){
7222  allocator->deleteObj(exp);
7223  return lib.error(Tokenizer::OPERATOR_COLON, recent_token);
7224  }
7225  save_token = readToken();
7226  Expression * exp2 = expectSingleExpression(scope, p);
7227  if(!exp2){
7228  return isError() ? lib.error() : lib.error(ERROR_EXPECT_EXPRESSION, save_token);
7229  }
7230  exp2 = expectExpressionValues(exp2, 1);
7231  exp = new (malloc(sizeof(Expression) OS_DBG_FILEPOS)) Expression(EXP_TYPE_OBJECT_SET_BY_EXP, name_token, exp, exp2 OS_DBG_FILEPOS);
7232  }else if(name_token->type == Tokenizer::NAME && name_token->str == allocator->core->strings->syntax_const){
7233  if(!expectToken(Tokenizer::NAME)){
7234  return lib.error();
7235  }
7236  name_token = recent_token;
7237  if(!expectToken(Tokenizer::OPERATOR_ASSIGN)){
7238  return lib.error();
7239  }
7240  // readToken(); // skip OPERATOR_COLON
7241  TokenData * save_token = readToken();
7242  exp = expectSingleExpression(scope, p);
7243  if(!exp){
7244  return isError() ? lib.error() : lib.error(ERROR_EXPECT_EXPRESSION, save_token);
7245  }
7246  exp = expectExpressionValues(exp, 1);
7247  exp = new (malloc(sizeof(Expression) OS_DBG_FILEPOS)) Expression(EXP_TYPE_OBJECT_CREATE_CONST, name_token, exp OS_DBG_FILEPOS);
7248  }else if(isNextToken(Tokenizer::OPERATOR_COLON) || isNextToken(Tokenizer::OPERATOR_ASSIGN)){
7249  ExpressionType exp_type = EXP_TYPE_OBJECT_SET_BY_NAME;
7250  switch(name_token->type){
7251  case Tokenizer::STRING:
7252  case Tokenizer::NAME:
7253  break;
7254 
7255  case Tokenizer::NUMBER:
7256  /* if(name_token->getFloat() != (OS_FLOAT)(OS_INT)name_token->getFloat()){
7257  // use it as EXP_TYPE_OBJECT_SET_BY_NAME
7258  break;
7259  } */
7260  exp_type = EXP_TYPE_OBJECT_SET_BY_INDEX;
7261  break;
7262 
7263  default:
7264  return lib.error(ERROR_SYNTAX, name_token);
7265  }
7266  readToken(); // skip OPERATOR_COLON
7267  TokenData * save_token = readToken();
7268  exp = expectSingleExpression(scope, p);
7269  if(!exp){
7270  return isError() ? lib.error() : lib.error(ERROR_EXPECT_EXPRESSION, save_token);
7271  }
7272  exp = expectExpressionValues(exp, 1);
7273  exp = new (malloc(sizeof(Expression) OS_DBG_FILEPOS)) Expression(exp_type, name_token, exp OS_DBG_FILEPOS);
7274  }else if(name_token->type == Tokenizer::OPERATOR_SUB || name_token->type == Tokenizer::OPERATOR_ADD){
7275  if(!expectToken(Tokenizer::NUMBER)){
7276  return lib.error();
7277  }
7278  if(name_token->type == Tokenizer::OPERATOR_SUB){
7279  name_token = recent_token;
7280  name_token->setFloat(-name_token->getFloat());
7281  }else{
7282  name_token = recent_token;
7283  }
7284  ExpressionType exp_type = EXP_TYPE_OBJECT_SET_BY_INDEX;
7285  if(isNextToken(Tokenizer::OPERATOR_COLON) || isNextToken(Tokenizer::OPERATOR_ASSIGN)){
7286  readToken(); // skip OPERATOR_COLON
7287  TokenData * save_token = readToken();
7288  exp = expectSingleExpression(scope, p);
7289  if(!exp){
7290  return isError() ? lib.error() : lib.error(ERROR_EXPECT_EXPRESSION, save_token);
7291  }
7292  exp = expectExpressionValues(exp, 1);
7293  exp = new (malloc(sizeof(Expression) OS_DBG_FILEPOS)) Expression(exp_type, name_token, exp OS_DBG_FILEPOS);
7294  }else{
7295  expectToken(Tokenizer::OPERATOR_ASSIGN);
7296  return lib.error();
7297  }
7298  }else{
7299  exp = expectSingleExpression(scope, p);
7300  if(!exp){
7301  return isError() ? lib.error() : lib.error(ERROR_EXPECT_EXPRESSION, name_token);
7302  }
7303  exp = expectExpressionValues(exp, 1);
7304  exp = new (malloc(sizeof(Expression) OS_DBG_FILEPOS)) Expression(EXP_TYPE_OBJECT_SET_BY_AUTO_INDEX, name_token, exp OS_DBG_FILEPOS);
7305  }
7306  OS_ASSERT(exp);
7307  lib.obj_exp->list.add(exp OS_DBG_FILEPOS);
7308  if(recent_token && recent_token->type == Tokenizer::END_CODE_BLOCK){
7309  readToken();
7310  return lib.finishValue(scope, org_p, allow_finish_exp);
7311  }
7312  if(!recent_token){
7313  return lib.error(Tokenizer::END_CODE_BLOCK, recent_token);
7314  }
7315 #ifdef OS_PARAMS_WITHOUT_SEPARATOR
7316  switch(recent_token->type){
7317  case Tokenizer::PARAM_SEPARATOR:
7318  case Tokenizer::CODE_SEPARATOR:
7319  readToken();
7320  }
7321 #else
7322  if(recent_token->type != Tokenizer::PARAM_SEPARATOR && recent_token->type != Tokenizer::CODE_SEPARATOR){
7323  return lib.error(Tokenizer::PARAM_SEPARATOR, recent_token);
7324  }
7325  readToken();
7326 #endif
7327  }
7328  return NULL; // shut up compiler
7329 }

7331 OS::Core::Compiler::Expression * OS::Core::Compiler::expectArrayExpression(Scope * scope, const Params& __p)
7332 {
7333  Params next_p = Params(__p).setAllowAssign(false).setAllowAutoCall(false);
7334  Expression * params = new (malloc(sizeof(Expression) OS_DBG_FILEPOS)) Expression(EXP_TYPE_ARRAY, recent_token);
7335  params->ret_values = 1;
7336  readToken();
7337  if(recent_token && recent_token->type == Tokenizer::END_ARRAY_BLOCK){
7338  readToken();
7339  return finishValueExpression(scope, params, next_p);
7340  }
7341  Params p = Params().setAllowBinaryOperator(true);
7342  for(int auto_index = 0;;){
7343  Expression * exp = expectSingleExpression(scope, p);
7344  if(!exp){
7345  if(isError()){
7346  allocator->deleteObj(params);
7347  return NULL;
7348  }
7349  if(!recent_token || recent_token->type != Tokenizer::END_ARRAY_BLOCK){
7350  setError(Tokenizer::END_ARRAY_BLOCK, recent_token);
7351  allocator->deleteObj(params);
7352  return NULL;
7353  }
7354  readToken();
7355  return finishValueExpression(scope, params, next_p);
7356  }
7357  exp = expectExpressionValues(exp, 1);
7358 
7359  TokenData * index_token = new (malloc(sizeof(TokenData) OS_DBG_FILEPOS)) TokenData(tokenizer->getTextData(), exp->token->str,
7360  Tokenizer::NUMBER, exp->token->line, exp->token->pos);
7361  index_token->setFloat((OS_FLOAT)(auto_index++));
7362  exp = new (malloc(sizeof(Expression) OS_DBG_FILEPOS)) Expression(EXP_TYPE_OBJECT_SET_BY_INDEX, index_token, exp OS_DBG_FILEPOS);
7363  index_token->release();
7364  params->list.add(exp OS_DBG_FILEPOS);
7365  if(recent_token && recent_token->type == Tokenizer::END_ARRAY_BLOCK){
7366  readToken();
7367  return finishValueExpression(scope, params, next_p);
7368  }
7369  if(!recent_token){
7370  setError(Tokenizer::END_ARRAY_BLOCK, recent_token);
7371  allocator->deleteObj(params);
7372  return NULL;
7373  }
7374 #ifdef OS_PARAMS_WITHOUT_SEPARATOR
7375  switch(recent_token->type){
7376  case Tokenizer::PARAM_SEPARATOR:
7377  case Tokenizer::CODE_SEPARATOR:
7378  readToken();
7379  }
7380 #else
7381  if(recent_token->type != Tokenizer::PARAM_SEPARATOR && recent_token->type != Tokenizer::CODE_SEPARATOR){
7382  setError(Tokenizer::PARAM_SEPARATOR, recent_token);
7383  allocator->deleteObj(params);
7384  return NULL;
7385  }
7386  readToken();
7387 #endif
7388  }
7389  return NULL; // shut up compiler
7390 }
7391 
7392 OS::Core::Compiler::Expression * OS::Core::Compiler::expectParamsExpression(Scope * scope)
7393 {
7394  struct Lib
7395  {
7396  static Expression * calcParamsExpression(Compiler * compiler, Scope * scope, Expression * params)
7397  {
7398  if(params->list.count > 1){
7399  for(int i = 0; i < params->list.count; i++){
7400  params->list[i] = compiler->expectExpressionValues(params->list[i], 1);
7401  }
7402  params->ret_values = params->list.count;
7403  }else if(params->list.count == 1){
7404  params->ret_values = params->list[0]->ret_values;
7405  }
7406  return params;
7407  }
7408  };
7409 
7410  Expression * params = new (malloc(sizeof(Expression) OS_DBG_FILEPOS)) Expression(EXP_TYPE_PARAMS, recent_token);
7411  bool is_dim = recent_token->type == Tokenizer::BEGIN_ARRAY_BLOCK;
7412  TokenType end_exp_type = is_dim ? Tokenizer::END_ARRAY_BLOCK : Tokenizer::END_BRACKET_BLOCK;
7413  readToken();
7414  if(recent_token && recent_token->type == end_exp_type){
7415  readToken();
7416  return Lib::calcParamsExpression(this, scope, params);
7417  }
7418  Params p = Params().setAllowBinaryOperator(true);
7419  for(;;){
7420  Expression * exp = expectSingleExpression(scope, p);
7421  if(!exp){
7422  if(isError()){
7423  allocator->deleteObj(params);
7424  return NULL;
7425  }
7426  if(!recent_token || recent_token->type != end_exp_type){
7427  setError(end_exp_type, recent_token);
7428  allocator->deleteObj(params);
7429  return NULL;
7430  }
7431  readToken();
7432  return Lib::calcParamsExpression(this, scope, params);
7433  }
7434  exp = expectExpressionValues(exp, 1);
7435  params->list.add(exp OS_DBG_FILEPOS);
7436 #ifdef OS_PARAMS_WITHOUT_SEPARATOR
7437  if(recent_token && (recent_token->type == Tokenizer::PARAM_SEPARATOR || recent_token->type == Tokenizer::CODE_SEPARATOR)){
7438  readToken();
7439  }
7440 #else
7441  if(recent_token && recent_token->type != end_exp_type){
7442  if(recent_token->type != Tokenizer::PARAM_SEPARATOR){
7443  setError(Tokenizer::PARAM_SEPARATOR, recent_token);
7444  allocator->deleteObj(params);
7445  return NULL;
7446  }
7447  readToken();
7448  }
7449 #endif
7450  if(recent_token && recent_token->type == end_exp_type){
7451  readToken();
7452  return Lib::calcParamsExpression(this, scope, params);
7453  }
7454  if(!recent_token){
7455  setError(end_exp_type, recent_token);
7456  allocator->deleteObj(params);
7457  return NULL;
7458  }
7459  }
7460  return NULL; // shut up compiler
7461 }
7462 
7463 OS::Core::Compiler::Expression * OS::Core::Compiler::expectBracketExpression(Scope * scope, const Params& p)
7464 {
7465  OS_ASSERT(recent_token && recent_token->type == Tokenizer::BEGIN_BRACKET_BLOCK);
7466  readToken();
7467  Expression * exp = expectSingleExpression(scope, Params()
7468  .setAllowBinaryOperator(true)
7469  .setAllowCall(true)
7470  .setAllowAutoCall(true));
7471  if(!exp){
7472  return NULL;
7473  }
7474  exp = newSingleValueExpression(exp);
7475  OS_ASSERT(exp->ret_values == 1);
7476  if(!recent_token){
7477  setError(Tokenizer::END_BRACKET_BLOCK, recent_token);
7478  allocator->deleteObj(exp);
7479  return NULL;
7480  }
7481  switch(recent_token->type){
7482  case Tokenizer::END_BRACKET_BLOCK:
7483  readToken();
7484  return finishValueExpression(scope, exp, p);
7485  }
7486  setError(Tokenizer::END_BRACKET_BLOCK, recent_token);
7487  allocator->deleteObj(exp);
7488  return NULL;
7489 }

7491 OS::Core::Compiler::Expression * OS::Core::Compiler::expectExtendsExpression(Scope * scope)
7492 {
7493  OS_ASSERT(recent_token && recent_token->str == allocator->core->strings->syntax_extends);
7494  TokenData * save_token = recent_token;
7495  if(!expectToken()){
7496  return NULL;
7497  }
7498  Params p;
7499  Expression * exp = expectSingleExpression(scope, p);
7500  if(!exp){
7501  return NULL;
7502  }
7503  if(exp->type == EXP_TYPE_CALL_AUTO_PARAM){
7504  OS_ASSERT(exp->list.count == 2);
7505  Expression * params = exp->list[1];
7506  OS_ASSERT(params->type == EXP_TYPE_PARAMS && params->list.count == 1);
7507  exp->list[1] = params->list[0];
7508  allocator->vectorClear(params->list);
7509  allocator->deleteObj(params);
7510  exp->type = EXP_TYPE_EXTENDS;
7511  exp->ret_values = 1;
7512  return exp;
7513  }
7514 #if 1
7515  setError(ERROR_SYNTAX, exp->token);
7516  allocator->deleteObj(exp);
7517  return NULL;
7518 #else // TODO: delete it???
7519  Expression * exp2 = expectSingleExpression(scope, p);
7520  if(!exp2){
7521  allocator->deleteObj(exp);
7522  return NULL;
7523  }
7524  exp = expectExpressionValues(exp, 1);
7525  exp2 = expectExpressionValues(exp2, 1);
7526  exp = new (malloc(sizeof(Expression) OS_DBG_FILEPOS)) Expression(EXP_TYPE_EXTENDS, save_token, exp, exp2 OS_DBG_FILEPOS);
7527  exp->ret_values = 1;
7528  return exp;
7529 #endif
7530 }

7532 OS::Core::Compiler::Expression * OS::Core::Compiler::finishQuestionOperator(Scope * scope, TokenData * token, Expression * exp, Expression * exp2)
7533 {
7534  ungetToken();
7535  if(!expectToken(Tokenizer::OPERATOR_COLON)){
7536  allocator->deleteObj(exp);
7537  allocator->deleteObj(exp2);
7538  return NULL;
7539  }
7540  if(!expectToken()){
7541  return NULL;
7542  }
7543  Expression * exp3 = expectSingleExpression(scope, Params().setAllowBinaryOperator(true));
7544  if(!exp3){
7545  allocator->deleteObj(exp);
7546  allocator->deleteObj(exp2);
7547  return NULL;
7548  }
7549  exp = expectExpressionValues(exp, 1);
7550  exp2 = expectExpressionValues(exp2, 1);
7551  exp3 = expectExpressionValues(exp3, 1);
7552  exp = new (malloc(sizeof(Expression) OS_DBG_FILEPOS)) Expression(EXP_TYPE_QUESTION, token, exp, exp2, exp3 OS_DBG_FILEPOS);
7553  exp->ret_values = 1;
7554  return exp;
7555 }

7557 OS::Core::Compiler::Expression * OS::Core::Compiler::expectDeleteExpression(Scope * scope)
7558 {
7559  OS_ASSERT(recent_token && recent_token->str == allocator->core->strings->syntax_delete);
7560  if(!expectToken()){
7561  return NULL;
7562  }
7563  Expression * exp = expectSingleExpression(scope, Params());
7564  if(!exp){
7565  return NULL;
7566  }
7567  if(exp->type == EXP_TYPE_INDIRECT){
7568  OS_ASSERT(exp->list.count == 2);
7569  Expression * field = exp->list[1];
7570  if(field->type == EXP_TYPE_NAME){
7571  field->type = EXP_TYPE_CONST_STRING;
7572  }
7573  exp->type = EXP_TYPE_DELETE;
7574  exp->ret_values = 0;
7575  return exp;
7576  }
7577  if(exp->type == EXP_TYPE_CALL_DIM){
7578  OS_ASSERT(exp->list.count == 2);
7579  Expression * params = exp->list[1];
7580  if(params->list.count == 1){
7581  exp->list[1] = params->list[0];
7582  allocator->vectorClear(params->list);
7583  allocator->deleteObj(params);
7584  exp->type = EXP_TYPE_DELETE;
7585  exp->ret_values = 0;
7586  return exp;
7587  }
7588  Expression * object = exp->list[0];
7589 
7590  String method_name = !params->list.count ? allocator->core->strings->__delempty : allocator->core->strings->__deldim;
7591  TokenData * token = new (malloc(sizeof(TokenData) OS_DBG_FILEPOS)) TokenData(tokenizer->getTextData(), method_name, Tokenizer::NAME, object->token->line, object->token->pos);
7592  Expression * exp_method_name = new (malloc(sizeof(Expression) OS_DBG_FILEPOS)) Expression(EXP_TYPE_CONST_STRING, token);
7593  exp_method_name->ret_values = 1;
7594  token->release();
7595 
7596  Expression * indirect = new (malloc(sizeof(Expression) OS_DBG_FILEPOS)) Expression(EXP_TYPE_INDIRECT, object->token, object, exp_method_name OS_DBG_FILEPOS);
7597  exp->list[0] = indirect;
7598  exp->type = EXP_TYPE_CALL;
7599  exp->ret_values = 1;
7600  return exp;
7601  }
7602  setError(ERROR_SYNTAX, exp->token);
7603  allocator->deleteObj(exp);
7604  return NULL;
7605 }
7606 
7607 OS::Core::Compiler::Expression * OS::Core::Compiler::expectFunctionExpression(Scope * parent)
7608 {
7609  Scope * scope = new (malloc(sizeof(Scope) OS_DBG_FILEPOS)) Scope(parent, EXP_TYPE_FUNCTION, recent_token);
7610  scope->function = scope;
7611  scope->ret_values = 1;
7612  Expression * name_exp = NULL;
7613  if(isNextToken(Tokenizer::NAME)){
7614  TokenData * token = readToken();
7615  if(isNextToken(Tokenizer::NAME)){
7616  String prefix(allocator);
7617  if(token->str == allocator->core->strings->syntax_get){
7618  prefix = allocator->core->strings->__getAt;
7619  }else if(token->str == allocator->core->strings->syntax_set){
7620  prefix = allocator->core->strings->__setAt;
7621  }else{
7622  setError(ERROR_EXPECT_GET_OR_SET, token);
7623  allocator->deleteObj(name_exp);
7624  allocator->deleteObj(scope);
7625  return NULL;
7626  }
7627  token = readToken();
7628  token->str = String(allocator, prefix, token->str);
7629  name_exp = new (malloc(sizeof(Expression) OS_DBG_FILEPOS)) Expression(EXP_TYPE_NAME, token);
7630  }else{
7631  name_exp = expectSingleExpression(parent, Params().setAllowCall(false));
7632  if(!name_exp || !name_exp->isWriteable()){
7633  setError(ERROR_EXPECT_WRITEABLE, token);
7634  allocator->deleteObj(name_exp);
7635  allocator->deleteObj(scope);
7636  return NULL;
7637  }
7638  ungetToken();
7639  }
7640  }
7641  if(!expectToken(Tokenizer::BEGIN_BRACKET_BLOCK)){
7642  allocator->deleteObj(scope);
7643  return NULL;
7644  }
7645  scope->addPreVars();
7646  for(;;){
7647  if(!readToken()){
7648  setError(ERROR_SYNTAX, recent_token);
7649  allocator->deleteObj(scope);
7650  return NULL;
7651  }
7652  switch(recent_token->type){
7653  case Tokenizer::END_BRACKET_BLOCK:
7654  break;
7655 
7656  case Tokenizer::NAME:
7657  scope->addLocalVar(recent_token->str, CVT_DYNAMIC);
7658  if(!readToken()){
7659  setError(ERROR_SYNTAX, recent_token);
7660  allocator->deleteObj(scope);
7661  return NULL;
7662  }
7663  if(recent_token->type == Tokenizer::END_BRACKET_BLOCK){
7664  break;
7665  }
7666 #ifdef OS_PARAMS_WITHOUT_SEPARATOR
7667  if(recent_token->type == Tokenizer::PARAM_SEPARATOR){
7668  continue;
7669  }
7670  ungetToken();
7671 #else
7672  if(recent_token->type != Tokenizer::PARAM_SEPARATOR){
7673  setError(Tokenizer::PARAM_SEPARATOR, recent_token);
7674  allocator->deleteObj(scope);
7675  return NULL;
7676  }
7677 #endif
7678  continue;
7679 
7680  default:
7681  setError(ERROR_SYNTAX, recent_token);
7682  allocator->deleteObj(scope);
7683  return NULL;
7684  }
7685  break;
7686  }
7687  scope->num_params = scope->num_locals;
7688  OS_ASSERT(recent_token && recent_token->type == Tokenizer::END_BRACKET_BLOCK);
7689  if(!expectToken(Tokenizer::BEGIN_CODE_BLOCK)){
7690  allocator->deleteObj(scope);
7691  return NULL;
7692  }
7693  scope->addPostVars();
7694  scope = expectCodeExpression(scope);
7695  if(!scope || !name_exp){
7696  return scope;
7697  }
7698  return newBinaryExpression(parent, EXP_TYPE_ASSIGN, name_exp->token, name_exp, scope);
7699 }
7700 
7701 OS::Core::Compiler::Expression * OS::Core::Compiler::expectFunctionSugarExpression(Scope * parent)
7702 {
7703  OS_ASSERT(recent_token && (recent_token->type == Tokenizer::OPERATOR_BIT_OR || recent_token->type == Tokenizer::OPERATOR_LOGIC_OR));
7704  Scope * scope = new (malloc(sizeof(Scope) OS_DBG_FILEPOS)) Scope(parent, EXP_TYPE_FUNCTION, recent_token);
7705  scope->function = scope;
7706  scope->ret_values = 1;
7707  scope->addPreVars();
7708  if(recent_token->type == Tokenizer::OPERATOR_BIT_OR)
7709  for(;;){
7710  if(!readToken()){
7711  setError(ERROR_SYNTAX, recent_token);
7712  allocator->deleteObj(scope);
7713  return NULL;
7714  }
7715  switch(recent_token->type){
7716  case Tokenizer::OPERATOR_BIT_OR:
7717  break;
7718 
7719  case Tokenizer::NAME:
7720  scope->addLocalVar(recent_token->str, CVT_DYNAMIC);
7721  if(!readToken()){
7722  setError(ERROR_SYNTAX, recent_token);
7723  allocator->deleteObj(scope);
7724  return NULL;
7725  }
7726  if(recent_token->type == Tokenizer::OPERATOR_BIT_OR){
7727  break;
7728  }
7729 #ifdef OS_PARAMS_WITHOUT_SEPARATOR
7730  if(recent_token->type == Tokenizer::PARAM_SEPARATOR){
7731  continue;
7732  }
7733  ungetToken();
7734 #else
7735  if(recent_token->type != Tokenizer::PARAM_SEPARATOR){
7736  setError(Tokenizer::PARAM_SEPARATOR, recent_token);
7737  allocator->deleteObj(scope);
7738  return NULL;
7739  }
7740 #endif
7741  continue;
7742 
7743  default:
7744  setError(ERROR_SYNTAX, recent_token);
7745  allocator->deleteObj(scope);
7746  return NULL;
7747  }
7748  break;
7749  }
7750  scope->num_params = scope->num_locals;
7751  OS_ASSERT(recent_token && (recent_token->type == Tokenizer::OPERATOR_BIT_OR || recent_token->type == Tokenizer::OPERATOR_LOGIC_OR));
7752  scope->addPostVars();
7753 
7754  if(!expectToken()){
7755  allocator->deleteObj(scope);
7756  return NULL;
7757  }
7758  scope->parser_started = true;
7759 
7760  Params p = Params()
7761  .setAllowAssign(true)
7762  .setAllowAutoCall(true)
7763  .setAllowBinaryOperator(true)
7764  .setAllowParams(true)
7765  .setAllowRootBlocks(true);
7766 
7767  Expression * exp;
7768  ExpressionList list(allocator);
7769  bool last_exp_exists = true;
7770  while(!isError()){
7771  exp = expectSingleExpression(scope, p);
7772  if(isError()){
7773  break;
7774  }
7775  if(exp){
7776  last_exp_exists = true;
7777  list.add(exp OS_DBG_FILEPOS);
7778  }else{
7779  last_exp_exists = false;
7780  }
7781  if(!recent_token)
7782  { // TODO: add more intellectual error reporting???
7783  setError(Tokenizer::END_CODE_BLOCK, exp->token); // use last expression token
7784  break;
7785  }
7786  TokenType token_type = recent_token->type;
7787  if(token_type == Tokenizer::CODE_SEPARATOR){
7788  if(!readToken()){
7789  break;
7790  }
7791  token_type = recent_token->type;
7792  }
7793  if(token_type == Tokenizer::END_ARRAY_BLOCK
7794  || token_type == Tokenizer::END_BRACKET_BLOCK
7795  || token_type == Tokenizer::END_CODE_BLOCK)
7796  {
7797  break;
7798  }
7799  }
7800  if(isError()){
7801  allocator->deleteObj(scope);
7802  return NULL;
7803  }
7804  if(!recent_token || recent_token->type != Tokenizer::END_CODE_BLOCK){
7805  setError(Tokenizer::END_CODE_BLOCK, recent_token);
7806  allocator->deleteObj(scope);
7807  return NULL;
7808  }
7809  if(!last_exp_exists && list.count > 0){
7810  list.add(new (malloc(sizeof(Expression) OS_DBG_FILEPOS)) Expression(EXP_TYPE_NOP, recent_token) OS_DBG_FILEPOS);
7811  }
7812  readToken();
7813 
7814  if(list.count == 0){
7815  return scope;
7816  }
7817  exp = newExpressionFromList(list, 1, true);
7818  switch(exp->type){
7819  case EXP_TYPE_CODE_LIST:
7820  scope->list.swap(exp->list);
7821  allocator->deleteObj(exp);
7822  break;
7823 
7824  default:
7825  scope->list.add(exp OS_DBG_FILEPOS);
7826  }
7827  if(scope->list.count > 0){
7828  Expression * last_exp = scope->list.lastElement();
7829  if(last_exp->ret_values == 1 && last_exp->type != EXP_TYPE_RETURN){
7830  scope->list.lastElement() = new (malloc(sizeof(Expression) OS_DBG_FILEPOS)) Expression(EXP_TYPE_RETURN, last_exp->token, last_exp OS_DBG_FILEPOS);
7831  scope->list.lastElement()->ret_values = 1;
7832  }
7833  }
7834  return scope;
7835 }
7836 
7837 OS::Core::Compiler::Expression * OS::Core::Compiler::expectFunctionBlockExpression(Scope * parent)
7838 {
7839  OS_ASSERT(recent_token && recent_token->type == Tokenizer::BEGIN_CODE_BLOCK);
7840  Scope * scope = new (malloc(sizeof(Scope) OS_DBG_FILEPOS)) Scope(parent, EXP_TYPE_FUNCTION, recent_token);
7841  scope->function = scope;
7842  scope->ret_values = 1;
7843  scope->addPreVars();
7844  scope->num_params = scope->num_locals;
7845  scope->addPostVars();
7846 
7847  if(!expectToken()){
7848  allocator->deleteObj(scope);
7849  return NULL;
7850  }
7851  scope->parser_started = true;
7852 
7853  Params p = Params()
7854  .setAllowAssign(true)
7855  .setAllowAutoCall(true)
7856  .setAllowBinaryOperator(true)
7857  .setAllowParams(true)
7858  .setAllowRootBlocks(true);
7859 
7860  Expression * exp;
7861  ExpressionList list(allocator);
7862  while(!isError()){
7863  exp = expectSingleExpression(scope, p);
7864  if(isError()){
7865  break;
7866  }
7867  if(exp){
7868  list.add(exp OS_DBG_FILEPOS);
7869  }
7870  TokenType token_type = recent_token->type;
7871  if(token_type == Tokenizer::CODE_SEPARATOR){
7872  if(!readToken()){
7873  break;
7874  }
7875  token_type = recent_token->type;
7876  }
7877  if(token_type == Tokenizer::END_ARRAY_BLOCK
7878  || token_type == Tokenizer::END_BRACKET_BLOCK
7879  || token_type == Tokenizer::END_CODE_BLOCK)
7880  {
7881  break;
7882  }
7883  }
7884  if(isError()){
7885  allocator->deleteObj(scope);
7886  return NULL;
7887  }
7888  if(!recent_token || recent_token->type != Tokenizer::END_CODE_BLOCK){
7889  setError(Tokenizer::END_CODE_BLOCK, recent_token);
7890  allocator->deleteObj(scope);
7891  return NULL;
7892  }
7893  readToken();
7894 
7895  if(list.count > 0){
7896  exp = newExpressionFromList(list, 1, true);
7897  switch(exp->type){
7898  case EXP_TYPE_CODE_LIST:
7899  scope->list.swap(exp->list);
7900  allocator->deleteObj(exp);
7901  break;
7902 
7903  default:
7904  scope->list.add(exp OS_DBG_FILEPOS);
7905  }
7906  if(scope->list.count > 0){
7907  Expression * last_exp = scope->list.lastElement();
7908  if(last_exp->ret_values == 1 && last_exp->type != EXP_TYPE_RETURN){
7909  scope->list.lastElement() = new (malloc(sizeof(Expression) OS_DBG_FILEPOS)) Expression(EXP_TYPE_RETURN, last_exp->token, last_exp OS_DBG_FILEPOS);
7910  scope->list.lastElement()->ret_values = 1;
7911  }
7912  }
7913  }
7914  exp = new (malloc(sizeof(Expression) OS_DBG_FILEPOS)) Expression(EXP_TYPE_CALL_METHOD, scope->token, scope OS_DBG_FILEPOS);
7915  {
7916  Expression * params = new (malloc(sizeof(Expression) OS_DBG_FILEPOS)) Expression(EXP_TYPE_PARAMS, exp->token);
7917 
7918  String method_name = allocator->core->strings->func_call;
7919  TokenData * token = new (malloc(sizeof(TokenData) OS_DBG_FILEPOS)) TokenData(tokenizer->getTextData(), method_name, Tokenizer::NAME, exp->token->line, exp->token->pos);
7920  Expression * exp_method_name = new (malloc(sizeof(Expression) OS_DBG_FILEPOS)) Expression(EXP_TYPE_CONST_STRING, token);
7921  exp_method_name->ret_values = 1;
7922  token->release();
7923 
7924  Expression * exp_this = new (malloc(sizeof(Expression) OS_DBG_FILEPOS)) Expression(EXP_TYPE_GET_THIS, exp->token);
7925  exp_this->ret_values = 1;
7926 
7927  params->list.add(exp_method_name OS_DBG_FILEPOS);
7928  params->list.add(exp_this OS_DBG_FILEPOS);
7929  params->ret_values = 2;
7930  exp->list.add(params OS_DBG_FILEPOS);
7931  }
7932  return exp;
7933 }
7934 
7935 OS::Core::Compiler::Expression * OS::Core::Compiler::expectVarExpression(Scope * scope)
7936 {
7937  OS_ASSERT(recent_token && (recent_token->str == allocator->core->strings->syntax_var
7938  || recent_token->str == allocator->core->strings->syntax_local));
7939  bool is_local_scope_var = recent_token->str == allocator->core->strings->syntax_local;
7940  if(!expectToken(Tokenizer::NAME)){
7941  return NULL;
7942  }
7943  Expression * name_exp;
7944  Expression * exp = new (malloc(sizeof(Expression) OS_DBG_FILEPOS)) Expression(EXP_TYPE_PARAMS, recent_token);
7945  exp->ret_values = 1;
7946  if(recent_token->str == allocator->core->strings->syntax_function){
7947  if(!expectToken(Tokenizer::NAME)){
7948  allocator->deleteObj(exp);
7949  return NULL;
7950  }
7951  TokenData * name_token;
7952  // TODO: is "function get" deprecated?
7953  if(recent_token->str == allocator->core->strings->syntax_get || recent_token->str == allocator->core->strings->syntax_set){
7954  bool is_getter = recent_token->str == allocator->core->strings->syntax_get;
7955  if(!expectToken(Tokenizer::NAME)){
7956  allocator->deleteObj(exp);
7957  return NULL;
7958  }
7959  if(!isVarNameValid(recent_token->str)){
7960  setError(ERROR_VAR_NAME, recent_token);
7961  allocator->deleteObj(exp);
7962  return NULL;
7963  }
7964  if(!expectToken(Tokenizer::BEGIN_BRACKET_BLOCK)){
7965  allocator->deleteObj(exp);
7966  return NULL;
7967  }
7968  ungetToken();
7969  ungetToken();
7970 
7971  name_token = tokenizer->removeToken(next_token_index-1); name_token->release();
7972  name_token = tokenizer->removeToken(next_token_index-1);
7973  if(is_getter){
7974  name_token->str = String(allocator, allocator->core->strings->__getAt, name_token->str);
7975  }else{
7976  name_token->str = String(allocator, allocator->core->strings->__setAt, name_token->str);
7977  }
7978  }else{
7979  if(!isVarNameValid(recent_token->str)){
7980  setError(ERROR_VAR_NAME, recent_token);
7981  allocator->deleteObj(exp);
7982  return NULL;
7983  }
7984  if(!expectToken(Tokenizer::BEGIN_BRACKET_BLOCK)){
7985  allocator->deleteObj(exp);
7986  return NULL;
7987  }
7988  ungetToken();
7989 
7990  name_token = tokenizer->removeToken(next_token_index-1);
7991  }
7992 
7993  name_exp = new (malloc(sizeof(Expression) OS_DBG_FILEPOS)) Expression(EXP_TYPE_NAME, name_token);
7994  name_exp->ret_values = 1;
7995  name_token->release();
7996 
7997  allocator->deleteObj(exp);
7998 
7999  ungetToken(); // return to function
8000 
8001  Expression * func_exp = expectFunctionExpression(scope);
8002  if(!func_exp){
8003  allocator->deleteObj(exp);
8004  return NULL;
8005  }
8006  OS_ASSERT(func_exp->type == EXP_TYPE_FUNCTION);
8007  exp = newBinaryExpression(scope, EXP_TYPE_ASSIGN, name_exp->token, name_exp, func_exp);
8008  }else{
8009  for(;;){
8010  if(!isVarNameValid(recent_token->str)){
8011  setError(ERROR_VAR_NAME, recent_token);
8012  allocator->deleteObj(exp);
8013  return NULL;
8014  }
8015  name_exp = new (malloc(sizeof(Expression) OS_DBG_FILEPOS)) Expression(EXP_TYPE_NAME, recent_token);
8016  name_exp->ret_values = 1;
8017 
8018  exp->list.add(name_exp OS_DBG_FILEPOS);
8019  exp->ret_values++;
8020 
8021  if(!readToken() || recent_token->type != Tokenizer::PARAM_SEPARATOR){
8022  break;
8023  }
8024  if(!expectToken(Tokenizer::NAME)){
8025  allocator->deleteObj(exp);
8026  return NULL;
8027  }
8028  }
8029 
8030  if(recent_token && recent_token->type == Tokenizer::OPERATOR_ASSIGN){
8031  bool is_finished;
8032  exp = finishBinaryOperator(scope, getOpcodeLevel(exp->type), exp, Params().setAllowParams(true).setAllowInOperator(true), is_finished);
8033  OS_ASSERT(is_finished);
8034  }
8035  }
8036  struct Lib {
8037  static void registerLocalVar(Compiler * compiler, Scope * scope, Expression * exp, bool is_local_scope_var)
8038  {
8039  if(is_local_scope_var){
8040  if(!compiler->findLocalVar(exp->local_var, scope, exp->token->str, exp->active_locals, false, true)){
8041  scope->addLocalVar(exp->token->str, exp->local_var);
8042  }
8043  }else{
8044  if(!compiler->findLocalVar(exp->local_var, scope->function, exp->token->str, exp->active_locals, false, true)){
8045  scope->function->addLocalVar(exp->token->str, exp->local_var);
8046  }
8047  }
8048  }
8049  };
8050  Expression * ret_exp = exp;
8051  while(exp){
8052  switch(exp->type){
8053  case EXP_TYPE_PARAMS:
8054  {
8055  Expression * params = exp;
8056  for(int i = 0; i < params->list.count; i++){
8057  exp = params->list[i];
8058  OS_ASSERT(exp->type == EXP_TYPE_NAME);
8059  if(exp->type == EXP_TYPE_NAME){
8060  Lib::registerLocalVar(this, scope, exp, is_local_scope_var);
8061  OS_ASSERT(exp->local_var.up_count == 0);
8062  exp->type = EXP_TYPE_NEW_LOCAL_VAR;
8063  exp->ret_values = 0;
8064  }
8065  }
8066  params->ret_values = 0;
8067  return params;
8068  }
8069 
8070  case EXP_TYPE_SET_LOCAL_VAR:
8071  for(;;){
8072  if(exp->local_var.up_scope_count == 0){
8073  }else{
8074  Lib::registerLocalVar(this, scope, exp, is_local_scope_var);
8075  }
8076  OS_ASSERT(exp->list.count == 1);
8077  exp = exp->list[0];
8078  switch(exp->type){
8079  case EXP_TYPE_SET_ENV_VAR:
8080  case EXP_TYPE_SET_LOCAL_VAR:
8081  break;
8082 
8083  default:
8084  return ret_exp;
8085  }
8086  break;
8087  }
8088  break;
8089 
8090  case EXP_TYPE_SET_ENV_VAR:
8091  for(;;){
8092  Lib::registerLocalVar(this, scope, exp, is_local_scope_var);
8093  exp->type = EXP_TYPE_SET_LOCAL_VAR;
8094  OS_ASSERT(exp->list.count == 1);
8095  exp = exp->list[0];
8096  switch(exp->type){
8097  case EXP_TYPE_SET_ENV_VAR:
8098  case EXP_TYPE_SET_LOCAL_VAR:
8099  break;
8100 
8101  default:
8102  return ret_exp;
8103  }
8104  break;
8105  }
8106  break;
8107 
8108  case EXP_TYPE_NAME:
8109  Lib::registerLocalVar(this, scope, exp, is_local_scope_var);
8110  OS_ASSERT(exp->local_var.up_count == 0);
8111  exp->type = EXP_TYPE_NEW_LOCAL_VAR;
8112  exp->ret_values = 0;
8113  return ret_exp;
8114 
8115  default:
8116  return ret_exp;
8117  }
8118  }
8119  return ret_exp;
8120 }

8122 OS::Core::Compiler::Expression * OS::Core::Compiler::expectWhileExpression(Scope * parent)
8123 {
8124  OS_ASSERT(recent_token && recent_token->str == allocator->core->strings->syntax_while);
8125 
8126  Scope * scope = new (malloc(sizeof(Scope) OS_DBG_FILEPOS)) Scope(parent, EXP_TYPE_SCOPE, recent_token);
8127  if(!expectToken(Tokenizer::BEGIN_BRACKET_BLOCK) || !expectToken()){
8128  allocator->deleteObj(scope);
8129  return NULL;
8130  }
8131  Expression * bool_exp = expectSingleExpression(scope, Params().setAllowAutoCall(true).setAllowBinaryOperator(true));
8132  if(!bool_exp){
8133  allocator->deleteObj(scope);
8134  return NULL;
8135  }
8136  if(!bool_exp->ret_values){
8137  setError(ERROR_EXPECT_VALUE, bool_exp->token);
8138  allocator->deleteObj(scope);
8139  allocator->deleteObj(bool_exp);
8140  return NULL;
8141  }
8142  bool_exp = expectExpressionValues(bool_exp, 1);
8143 
8144  if(recent_token->type != Tokenizer::END_BRACKET_BLOCK){
8145  setError(Tokenizer::END_BRACKET_BLOCK, recent_token);
8146  allocator->deleteObj(scope);
8147  allocator->deleteObj(bool_exp);
8148  return NULL;
8149  }
8150  readToken();
8151 
8152  Scope * loop_scope = new (malloc(sizeof(Scope) OS_DBG_FILEPOS)) Scope(scope, EXP_TYPE_FOR_LOOP_SCOPE, recent_token);
8153  Expression * body_exp = expectSingleExpression(loop_scope, true, true);
8154  if(!body_exp){
8155  allocator->deleteObj(scope);
8156  allocator->deleteObj(bool_exp);
8157  allocator->deleteObj(loop_scope);
8158  return NULL;
8159  }
8160  body_exp = expectExpressionValues(body_exp, 0);
8161 
8162  Expression * not_exp = new (malloc(sizeof(Expression) OS_DBG_FILEPOS)) Expression(EXP_TYPE_LOGIC_NOT, bool_exp->token, bool_exp OS_DBG_FILEPOS);
8163  not_exp->ret_values = 1;
8164 
8165  Expression * break_exp = new (malloc(sizeof(Expression) OS_DBG_FILEPOS)) Expression(EXP_TYPE_BREAK, bool_exp->token);
8166  Expression * if_exp = new (malloc(sizeof(Expression) OS_DBG_FILEPOS)) Expression(EXP_TYPE_IF, bool_exp->token, not_exp, break_exp OS_DBG_FILEPOS);
8167 
8168  loop_scope->list.add(if_exp OS_DBG_FILEPOS);
8169 
8170  loop_scope->list.add(body_exp OS_DBG_FILEPOS);
8171 
8172  Expression * post_exp = new (malloc(sizeof(Expression) OS_DBG_FILEPOS)) Expression(EXP_TYPE_NOP, bool_exp->token);
8173  loop_scope->list.add(post_exp OS_DBG_FILEPOS);
8174 
8175  Expression * pre_exp = new (malloc(sizeof(Expression) OS_DBG_FILEPOS)) Expression(EXP_TYPE_NOP, bool_exp->token);
8176  scope->list.add(pre_exp OS_DBG_FILEPOS);
8177  scope->list.add(loop_scope OS_DBG_FILEPOS);
8178  return scope;
8179 }

8181 OS::Core::Compiler::Expression * OS::Core::Compiler::expectDoExpression(Scope * parent)
8182 {
8183  OS_ASSERT(recent_token && recent_token->str == allocator->core->strings->syntax_do);
8184 
8185  Scope * scope = new (malloc(sizeof(Scope) OS_DBG_FILEPOS)) Scope(parent, EXP_TYPE_SCOPE, recent_token);
8186  if(!expectToken()){
8187  allocator->deleteObj(scope);
8188  return NULL;
8189  }
8190 
8191  Scope * loop_scope = new (malloc(sizeof(Scope) OS_DBG_FILEPOS)) Scope(scope, EXP_TYPE_FOR_LOOP_SCOPE, recent_token);
8192  Expression * body_exp = expectSingleExpression(loop_scope, true, true);
8193  if(!body_exp){
8194  allocator->deleteObj(scope);
8195  allocator->deleteObj(loop_scope);
8196  return NULL;
8197  }
8198  body_exp = expectExpressionValues(body_exp, 0);
8199 
8200  if(recent_token && recent_token->type == Tokenizer::END_CODE_BLOCK){
8201  readToken();
8202  }
8203  ungetToken();
8204  if(!expectToken() || recent_token->type != Tokenizer::NAME || recent_token->str != allocator->core->strings->syntax_while){
8205  setError(allocator->core->strings->syntax_while, recent_token);
8206  allocator->deleteObj(scope);
8207  allocator->deleteObj(loop_scope);
8208  allocator->deleteObj(body_exp);
8209  return NULL;
8210  }
8211  if(!expectToken(Tokenizer::BEGIN_BRACKET_BLOCK) || !expectToken()){
8212  allocator->deleteObj(scope);
8213  allocator->deleteObj(loop_scope);
8214  allocator->deleteObj(body_exp);
8215  return NULL;
8216  }
8217 
8218  Expression * bool_exp = expectSingleExpression(scope, Params().setAllowAutoCall(true).setAllowBinaryOperator(true));
8219  if(!bool_exp){
8220  allocator->deleteObj(scope);
8221  allocator->deleteObj(loop_scope);
8222  allocator->deleteObj(body_exp);
8223  return NULL;
8224  }
8225  if(!bool_exp->ret_values){
8226  setError(ERROR_EXPECT_VALUE, bool_exp->token);
8227  allocator->deleteObj(scope);
8228  allocator->deleteObj(loop_scope);
8229  allocator->deleteObj(body_exp);
8230  allocator->deleteObj(bool_exp);
8231  return NULL;
8232  }
8233  bool_exp = expectExpressionValues(bool_exp, 1);
8234 
8235  if(recent_token->type != Tokenizer::END_BRACKET_BLOCK){
8236  setError(Tokenizer::END_BRACKET_BLOCK, recent_token);
8237  allocator->deleteObj(scope);
8238  allocator->deleteObj(loop_scope);
8239  allocator->deleteObj(body_exp);
8240  allocator->deleteObj(bool_exp);
8241  return NULL;
8242  }
8243  readToken();
8244 
8245  Expression * not_exp = new (malloc(sizeof(Expression) OS_DBG_FILEPOS)) Expression(EXP_TYPE_LOGIC_NOT, bool_exp->token, bool_exp OS_DBG_FILEPOS);
8246  not_exp->ret_values = 1;
8247 
8248  Expression * break_exp = new (malloc(sizeof(Expression) OS_DBG_FILEPOS)) Expression(EXP_TYPE_BREAK, bool_exp->token);
8249  Expression * if_exp = new (malloc(sizeof(Expression) OS_DBG_FILEPOS)) Expression(EXP_TYPE_IF, bool_exp->token, not_exp, break_exp OS_DBG_FILEPOS);
8250 
8251  Expression * nop_exp = new (malloc(sizeof(Expression) OS_DBG_FILEPOS)) Expression(EXP_TYPE_NOP, bool_exp->token);
8252  loop_scope->list.add(nop_exp OS_DBG_FILEPOS);
8253 
8254  loop_scope->list.add(body_exp OS_DBG_FILEPOS);
8255 
8256  Expression * post_exp = if_exp;
8257  loop_scope->list.add(post_exp OS_DBG_FILEPOS);
8258 
8259  Expression * pre_exp = new (malloc(sizeof(Expression) OS_DBG_FILEPOS)) Expression(EXP_TYPE_NOP, bool_exp->token);
8260  scope->list.add(pre_exp OS_DBG_FILEPOS);
8261  scope->list.add(loop_scope OS_DBG_FILEPOS);
8262  return scope;
8263 }
